37379 var JpxImage = (function JpxImageClosure() {
37380   // Table E.1
37381   var SubbandsGainLog2 = {
37382     'LL': 0,
37383     'LH': 1,
37384     'HL': 1,
37385     'HH': 2
37386   };
37387   function JpxImage() {
37388     this.failOnCorruptedImage = false;
37389   }
37390   JpxImage.prototype = {
37391     load: function JpxImage_load(url) {
37392       var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
37393       xhr.open('GET', url, true);
37394       xhr.responseType = 'arraybuffer';
37395       xhr.onload = (function() {
37396         // TODO catch parse error
37397         var data = new Uint8Array(xhr.response || xhr.mozResponseArrayBuffer);
37398         this.parse(data);
37399         if (this.onload)
37400           this.onload();
37401       }).bind(this);
37402       xhr.send(null);
37403     },
37404     parse: function JpxImage_parse(data) {
37405       function readUint(data, offset, bytes) {
37406         var n = 0;
37407         for (var i = 0; i < bytes; i++)
37408           n = n * 256 + (data[offset + i] & 0xFF);
37409         return n;
37410       }
37411       var position = 0, length = data.length;
37412       while (position < length) {
37413         var headerSize = 8;
37414         var lbox = readUint(data, position, 4);
37415         var tbox = readUint(data, position + 4, 4);
37416         position += headerSize;
37417         if (lbox == 1) {
37418           lbox = readUint(data, position, 8);
37419           position += 8;
37420           headerSize += 8;
37421         }
37422         if (lbox === 0)
37423           lbox = length - position + headerSize;
37424         if (lbox < headerSize)
37425           error('JPX error: Invalid box field size');
37426         var dataLength = lbox - headerSize;
37427         var jumpDataLength = true;
37428         switch (tbox) {
37429           case 0x6A501A1A: // 'jP\032\032'
37430             // TODO
37431             break;
37432           case 0x6A703268: // 'jp2h'
37433             jumpDataLength = false; // parsing child boxes
37434             break;
37435           case 0x636F6C72: // 'colr'
37436             // TODO
37437             break;
37438           case 0x6A703263: // 'jp2c'
37439             this.parseCodestream(data, position, position + dataLength);
37440             break;
37441         }
37442         if (jumpDataLength)
37443           position += dataLength;
37444       }
37445     },
37446     parseCodestream: function JpxImage_parseCodestream(data, start, end) {
37447       var context = {};
37448       try {
37449         var position = start;
37450         while (position < end) {
37451           var code = readUint16(data, position);
37452           position += 2;
37453 
37454           var length = 0, j;
37455           switch (code) {
37456             case 0xFF4F: // Start of codestream (SOC)
37457               context.mainHeader = true;
37458               break;
37459             case 0xFFD9: // End of codestream (EOC)
37460               break;
37461             case 0xFF51: // Image and tile size (SIZ)
37462               length = readUint16(data, position);
37463               var siz = {};
37464               siz.Xsiz = readUint32(data, position + 4);
37465               siz.Ysiz = readUint32(data, position + 8);
37466               siz.XOsiz = readUint32(data, position + 12);
37467               siz.YOsiz = readUint32(data, position + 16);
37468               siz.XTsiz = readUint32(data, position + 20);
37469               siz.YTsiz = readUint32(data, position + 24);
37470               siz.XTOsiz = readUint32(data, position + 28);
37471               siz.YTOsiz = readUint32(data, position + 32);
37472               var componentsCount = readUint16(data, position + 36);
37473               siz.Csiz = componentsCount;
37474               var components = [];
37475               j = position + 38;
37476               for (var i = 0; i < componentsCount; i++) {
37477                 var component = {
37478                   precision: (data[j] & 0x7F) + 1,
37479                   isSigned: !!(data[j] & 0x80),
37480                   XRsiz: data[j + 1],
37481                   YRsiz: data[j + 1]
37482                 };
37483                 calculateComponentDimensions(component, siz);
37484                 components.push(component);
37485               }
37486               context.SIZ = siz;
37487               context.components = components;
37488               calculateTileGrids(context, components);
37489               context.QCC = [];
37490               context.COC = [];
37491               break;
37492             case 0xFF5C: // Quantization default (QCD)
37493               length = readUint16(data, position);
37494               var qcd = {};
37495               j = position + 2;
37496               var sqcd = data[j++];
37497               var spqcdSize, scalarExpounded;
37498               switch (sqcd & 0x1F) {
37499                 case 0:
37500                   spqcdSize = 8;
37501                   scalarExpounded = true;
37502                   break;
37503                 case 1:
37504                   spqcdSize = 16;
37505                   scalarExpounded = false;
37506                   break;
37507                 case 2:
37508                   spqcdSize = 16;
37509                   scalarExpounded = true;
37510                   break;
37511                 default:
37512                   throw 'Invalid SQcd value ' + sqcd;
37513               }
37514               qcd.noQuantization = spqcdSize == 8;
37515               qcd.scalarExpounded = scalarExpounded;
37516               qcd.guardBits = sqcd >> 5;
37517               var spqcds = [];
37518               while (j < length + position) {
37519                 var spqcd = {};
37520                 if (spqcdSize == 8) {
37521                   spqcd.epsilon = data[j++] >> 3;
37522                   spqcd.mu = 0;
37523                 } else {
37524                   spqcd.epsilon = data[j] >> 3;
37525                   spqcd.mu = ((data[j] & 0x7) << 8) | data[j + 1];
37526                   j += 2;
37527                 }
37528                 spqcds.push(spqcd);
37529               }
37530               qcd.SPqcds = spqcds;
37531               if (context.mainHeader)
37532                 context.QCD = qcd;
37533               else {
37534                 context.currentTile.QCD = qcd;
37535                 context.currentTile.QCC = [];
37536               }
37537               break;
37538             case 0xFF5D: // Quantization component (QCC)
37539               length = readUint16(data, position);
37540               var qcc = {};
37541               j = position + 2;
37542               var cqcc;
37543               if (context.SIZ.Csiz < 257)
37544                 cqcc = data[j++];
37545               else {
37546                 cqcc = readUint16(data, j);
37547                 j += 2;
37548               }
37549               var sqcd = data[j++];
37550               var spqcdSize, scalarExpounded;
37551               switch (sqcd & 0x1F) {
37552                 case 0:
37553                   spqcdSize = 8;
37554                   scalarExpounded = true;
37555                   break;
37556                 case 1:
37557                   spqcdSize = 16;
37558                   scalarExpounded = false;
37559                   break;
37560                 case 2:
37561                   spqcdSize = 16;
37562                   scalarExpounded = true;
37563                   break;
37564                 default:
37565                   throw 'Invalid SQcd value ' + sqcd;
37566               }
37567               qcc.noQuantization = spqcdSize == 8;
37568               qcc.scalarExpounded = scalarExpounded;
37569               qcc.guardBits = sqcd >> 5;
37570               var spqcds = [];
37571               while (j < length + position) {
37572                 var spqcd = {};
37573                 if (spqcdSize == 8) {
37574                   spqcd.epsilon = data[j++] >> 3;
37575                   spqcd.mu = 0;
37576                 } else {
37577                   spqcd.epsilon = data[j] >> 3;
37578                   spqcd.mu = ((data[j] & 0x7) << 8) | data[j + 1];
37579                   j += 2;
37580                 }
37581                 spqcds.push(spqcd);
37582               }
37583               qcc.SPqcds = spqcds;
37584               if (context.mainHeader)
37585                 context.QCC[cqcc] = qcc;
37586               else
37587                 context.currentTile.QCC[cqcc] = qcc;
37588               break;
37589             case 0xFF52: // Coding style default (COD)
37590               length = readUint16(data, position);
37591               var cod = {};
37592               j = position + 2;
37593               var scod = data[j++];
37594               cod.entropyCoderWithCustomPrecincts = !!(scod & 1);
37595               cod.sopMarkerUsed = !!(scod & 2);
37596               cod.ephMarkerUsed = !!(scod & 4);
37597               var codingStyle = {};
37598               cod.progressionOrder = data[j++];
37599               cod.layersCount = readUint16(data, j);
37600               j += 2;
37601               cod.multipleComponentTransform = data[j++];
37602 
37603               cod.decompositionLevelsCount = data[j++];
37604               cod.xcb = (data[j++] & 0xF) + 2;
37605               cod.ycb = (data[j++] & 0xF) + 2;
37606               var blockStyle = data[j++];
37607               cod.selectiveArithmeticCodingBypass = !!(blockStyle & 1);
37608               cod.resetContextProbabilities = !!(blockStyle & 2);
37609               cod.terminationOnEachCodingPass = !!(blockStyle & 4);
37610               cod.verticalyStripe = !!(blockStyle & 8);
37611               cod.predictableTermination = !!(blockStyle & 16);
37612               cod.segmentationSymbolUsed = !!(blockStyle & 32);
37613               cod.transformation = data[j++];
37614               if (cod.entropyCoderWithCustomPrecincts) {
37615                 var precinctsSizes = {};
37616                 while (j < length + position) {
37617                   var precinctsSize = data[j];
37618                   precinctsSizes.push({
37619                     PPx: precinctsSize & 0xF,
37620                     PPy: precinctsSize >> 4
37621                   });
37622                 }
37623                 cod.precinctsSizes = precinctsSizes;
37624               }
37625 
37626               if (cod.sopMarkerUsed || cod.ephMarkerUsed ||
37627                   cod.selectiveArithmeticCodingBypass ||
37628                   cod.resetContextProbabilities ||
37629                   cod.terminationOnEachCodingPass ||
37630                   cod.verticalyStripe || cod.predictableTermination)
37631                 throw 'Unsupported COD options: ' +
37632                   globalScope.JSON.stringify(cod);
37633 
37634               if (context.mainHeader)
37635                 context.COD = cod;
37636               else {
37637                 context.currentTile.COD = cod;
37638                 context.currentTile.COC = [];
37639               }
37640               break;
37641             case 0xFF90: // Start of tile-part (SOT)
37642               length = readUint16(data, position);
37643               var tile = {};
37644               tile.index = readUint16(data, position + 2);
37645               tile.length = readUint32(data, position + 4);
37646               tile.dataEnd = tile.length + position - 2;
37647               tile.partIndex = data[position + 8];
37648               tile.partsCount = data[position + 9];
37649 
37650               context.mainHeader = false;
37651               if (tile.partIndex === 0) {
37652                 // reset component specific settings
37653                 tile.COD = context.COD;
37654                 tile.COC = context.COC.slice(0); // clone of the global COC
37655                 tile.QCD = context.QCD;
37656                 tile.QCC = context.QCC.slice(0); // clone of the global COC
37657               }
37658               context.currentTile = tile;
37659               break;
37660             case 0xFF93: // Start of data (SOD)
37661               var tile = context.currentTile;
37662               if (tile.partIndex === 0) {
37663                 initializeTile(context, tile.index);
37664                 buildPackets(context);
37665               }
37666 
37667               // moving to the end of the data
37668               length = tile.dataEnd - position;
37669 
37670               parseTilePackets(context, data, position, length);
37671               break;
37672             case 0xFF64: // Comment (COM)
37673               length = readUint16(data, position);
37674               // skipping content
37675               break;
37676             default:
37677               throw 'Unknown codestream code: ' + code.toString(16);
37678           }
37679           position += length;
37680         }
37681       } catch (e) {
37682         if (this.failOnCorruptedImage)
37683           error('JPX error: ' + e);
37684         else
37685           warn('JPX error: ' + e + '. Trying to recover');
37686       }
37687       this.tiles = transformComponents(context);
37688       this.width = context.SIZ.Xsiz - context.SIZ.XOsiz;
37689       this.height = context.SIZ.Ysiz - context.SIZ.YOsiz;
37690       this.componentsCount = context.SIZ.Csiz;
37691     }
37692   };
37693   function readUint32(data, offset) {
37694     return (data[offset] << 24) | (data[offset + 1] << 16) |
37695       (data[offset + 2] << 8) | data[offset + 3];
37696   }
37697   function readUint16(data, offset) {
37698     return (data[offset] << 8) | data[offset + 1];
37699   }
37700   function log2(x) {
37701     var n = 1, i = 0;
37702     while (x > n) {
37703       n <<= 1;
37704       i++;
37705     }
37706     return i;
37707   }
37708   function calculateComponentDimensions(component, siz) {
37709     // Section B.2 Component mapping
37710     component.x0 = Math.ceil(siz.XOsiz / component.XRsiz);
37711     component.x1 = Math.ceil(siz.Xsiz / component.XRsiz);
37712     component.y0 = Math.ceil(siz.YOsiz / component.YRsiz);
37713     component.y1 = Math.ceil(siz.Ysiz / component.YRsiz);
37714     component.width = component.x1 - component.x0;
37715     component.height = component.y1 - component.y0;
37716   }
37717   function calculateTileGrids(context, components) {
37718     var siz = context.SIZ;
37719     // Section B.3 Division into tile and tile-components
37720     var tiles = [];
37721     var numXtiles = Math.ceil((siz.Xsiz - siz.XTOsiz) / siz.XTsiz);
37722     var numYtiles = Math.ceil((siz.Ysiz - siz.YTOsiz) / siz.YTsiz);
37723     for (var q = 0; q < numYtiles; q++) {
37724       for (var p = 0; p < numXtiles; p++) {
37725         var tile = {};
37726         tile.tx0 = Math.max(siz.XTOsiz + p * siz.XTsiz, siz.XOsiz);
37727         tile.ty0 = Math.max(siz.YTOsiz + q * siz.YTsiz, siz.YOsiz);
37728         tile.tx1 = Math.min(siz.XTOsiz + (p + 1) * siz.XTsiz, siz.Xsiz);
37729         tile.ty1 = Math.min(siz.YTOsiz + (q + 1) * siz.YTsiz, siz.Ysiz);
37730         tile.width = tile.tx1 - tile.tx0;
37731         tile.height = tile.ty1 - tile.ty0;
37732         tile.components = [];
37733         tiles.push(tile);
37734       }
37735     }
37736     context.tiles = tiles;
37737 
37738     var componentsCount = siz.Csiz;
37739     for (var i = 0, ii = componentsCount; i < ii; i++) {
37740       var component = components[i];
37741       var tileComponents = [];
37742       for (var j = 0, jj = tiles.length; j < jj; j++) {
37743         var tileComponent = {}, tile = tiles[j];
37744         tileComponent.tcx0 = Math.ceil(tile.tx0 / component.XRsiz);
37745         tileComponent.tcy0 = Math.ceil(tile.ty0 / component.YRsiz);
37746         tileComponent.tcx1 = Math.ceil(tile.tx1 / component.XRsiz);
37747         tileComponent.tcy1 = Math.ceil(tile.ty1 / component.YRsiz);
37748         tileComponent.width = tileComponent.tcx1 - tileComponent.tcx0;
37749         tileComponent.height = tileComponent.tcy1 - tileComponent.tcy0;
37750         tile.components[i] = tileComponent;
37751       }
37752     }
37753   }
37754   function getBlocksDimensions(context, component, r) {
37755     var codOrCoc = component.codingStyleParameters;
37756     var result = {};
37757     if (!codOrCoc.entropyCoderWithCustomPrecincts) {
37758       result.PPx = 15;
37759       result.PPy = 15;
37760     } else {
37761       result.PPx = codOrCoc.precinctsSizes[r].PPx;
37762       result.PPy = codOrCoc.precinctsSizes[r].PPy;
37763     }
37764     // calculate codeblock size as described in section B.7
37765     result.xcb_ = r > 0 ? Math.min(codOrCoc.xcb, result.PPx - 1) :
37766       Math.min(codOrCoc.xcb, result.PPx);
37767     result.ycb_ = r > 0 ? Math.min(codOrCoc.ycb, result.PPy - 1) :
37768       Math.min(codOrCoc.ycb, result.PPy);
37769     return result;
37770   }
37771   function buildPrecincts(context, resolution, dimensions) {
37772     // Section B.6 Division resolution to precincts
37773     var precinctWidth = 1 << dimensions.PPx;
37774     var precinctHeight = 1 << dimensions.PPy;
37775     var numprecinctswide = resolution.trx1 > resolution.trx0 ?
37776       Math.ceil(resolution.trx1 / precinctWidth) -
37777       Math.floor(resolution.trx0 / precinctWidth) : 0;
37778     var numprecinctshigh = resolution.try1 > resolution.try0 ?
37779       Math.ceil(resolution.try1 / precinctHeight) -
37780       Math.floor(resolution.try0 / precinctHeight) : 0;
37781     var numprecincts = numprecinctswide * numprecinctshigh;
37782     var precinctXOffset = Math.floor(resolution.trx0 / precinctWidth) *
37783       precinctWidth;
37784     var precinctYOffset = Math.floor(resolution.try0 / precinctHeight) *
37785       precinctHeight;
37786     resolution.precinctParameters = {
37787       precinctXOffset: precinctXOffset,
37788       precinctYOffset: precinctYOffset,
37789       precinctWidth: precinctWidth,
37790       precinctHeight: precinctHeight,
37791       numprecinctswide: numprecinctswide,
37792       numprecinctshigh: numprecinctshigh,
37793       numprecincts: numprecincts
37794     };
37795   }
37796   function buildCodeblocks(context, subband, dimensions) {
37797     // Section B.7 Division sub-band into code-blocks
37798     var xcb_ = dimensions.xcb_;
37799     var ycb_ = dimensions.ycb_;
37800     var codeblockWidth = 1 << xcb_;
37801     var codeblockHeight = 1 << ycb_;
37802     var cbx0 = Math.floor(subband.tbx0 / codeblockWidth);
37803     var cby0 = Math.floor(subband.tby0 / codeblockHeight);
37804     var cbx1 = Math.ceil(subband.tbx1 / codeblockWidth);
37805     var cby1 = Math.ceil(subband.tby1 / codeblockHeight);
37806     var precinctParameters = subband.resolution.precinctParameters;
37807     var codeblocks = [];
37808     var precincts = [];
37809     for (var j = cby0; j < cby1; j++) {
37810       for (var i = cbx0; i < cbx1; i++) {
37811         var codeblock = {
37812           cbx: i,
37813           cby: j,
37814           tbx0: codeblockWidth * i,
37815           tby0: codeblockHeight * j,
37816           tbx1: codeblockWidth * (i + 1),
37817           tby1: codeblockHeight * (j + 1)
37818         };
37819         // calculate precinct number
37820         var pi = Math.floor((codeblock.tbx0 -
37821           precinctParameters.precinctXOffset) /
37822           precinctParameters.precinctWidth);
37823         var pj = Math.floor((codeblock.tby0 -
37824           precinctParameters.precinctYOffset) /
37825           precinctParameters.precinctHeight);
37826         var precinctNumber = pj +
37827           pi * precinctParameters.numprecinctswide;
37828         codeblock.tbx0_ = Math.max(subband.tbx0, codeblock.tbx0);
37829         codeblock.tby0_ = Math.max(subband.tby0, codeblock.tby0);
37830         codeblock.tbx1_ = Math.min(subband.tbx1, codeblock.tbx1);
37831         codeblock.tby1_ = Math.min(subband.tby1, codeblock.tby1);
37832         codeblock.precinctNumber = precinctNumber;
37833         codeblock.subbandType = subband.type;
37834         var coefficientsLength = (codeblock.tbx1_ - codeblock.tbx0_) *
37835           (codeblock.tby1_ - codeblock.tby0_);
37836         codeblock.Lblock = 3;
37837         codeblocks.push(codeblock);
37838         // building precinct for the sub-band
37839         var precinct;
37840         if (precinctNumber in precincts) {
37841           precinct = precincts[precinctNumber];
37842           precinct.cbxMin = Math.min(precinct.cbxMin, i);
37843           precinct.cbyMin = Math.min(precinct.cbyMin, j);
37844           precinct.cbxMax = Math.max(precinct.cbxMax, i);
37845           precinct.cbyMax = Math.max(precinct.cbyMax, j);
37846         } else {
37847           precincts[precinctNumber] = precinct = {
37848             cbxMin: i,
37849             cbyMin: j,
37850             cbxMax: i,
37851             cbyMax: j
37852           };
37853         }
37854         codeblock.precinct = precinct;
37855       }
37856     }
37857     subband.codeblockParameters = {
37858       codeblockWidth: xcb_,
37859       codeblockHeight: ycb_,
37860       numcodeblockwide: cbx1 - cbx0 + 1,
37861       numcodeblockhigh: cby1 - cby1 + 1
37862     };
37863     subband.codeblocks = codeblocks;
37864     for (var i = 0, ii = codeblocks.length; i < ii; i++) {
37865       var codeblock = codeblocks[i];
37866       var precinctNumber = codeblock.precinctNumber;
37867     }
37868     subband.precincts = precincts;
37869   }
37870   function createPacket(resolution, precinctNumber, layerNumber) {
37871     var precinctCodeblocks = [];
37872     // Section B.10.8 Order of info in packet
37873     var subbands = resolution.subbands;
37874     // sub-bands already ordered in 'LL', 'HL', 'LH', and 'HH' sequence
37875     for (var i = 0, ii = subbands.length; i < ii; i++) {
37876       var subband = subbands[i];
37877       var codeblocks = subband.codeblocks;
37878       for (var j = 0, jj = codeblocks.length; j < jj; j++) {
37879         var codeblock = codeblocks[j];
37880         if (codeblock.precinctNumber != precinctNumber)
37881           continue;
37882         precinctCodeblocks.push(codeblock);
37883       }
37884     }
37885     return {
37886       layerNumber: layerNumber,
37887       codeblocks: precinctCodeblocks
37888     };
37889   }
37890   function LayerResolutionComponentPositionIterator(context) {
37891     var siz = context.SIZ;
37892     var tileIndex = context.currentTile.index;
37893     var tile = context.tiles[tileIndex];
37894     var layersCount = tile.codingStyleDefaultParameters.layersCount;
37895     var componentsCount = siz.Csiz;
37896     var maxDecompositionLevelsCount = 0;
37897     for (var q = 0; q < componentsCount; q++) {
37898       maxDecompositionLevelsCount = Math.max(maxDecompositionLevelsCount,
37899         tile.components[q].codingStyleParameters.decompositionLevelsCount);
37900     }
37901 
37902     var l = 0, r = 0, i = 0, k = 0;
37903 
37904     this.nextPacket = function JpxImage_nextPacket() {
37905       // Section B.12.1.1 Layer-resolution-component-position
37906       for (; l < layersCount; l++) {
37907         for (; r <= maxDecompositionLevelsCount; r++) {
37908           for (; i < componentsCount; i++) {
37909             var component = tile.components[i];
37910             if (r > component.codingStyleParameters.decompositionLevelsCount)
37911               continue;
37912 
37913             var resolution = component.resolutions[r];
37914             var numprecincts = resolution.precinctParameters.numprecincts;
37915             for (; k < numprecincts;) {
37916               var packet = createPacket(resolution, k, l);
37917               k++;
37918               return packet;
37919             }
37920             k = 0;
37921           }
37922           i = 0;
37923         }
37924         r = 0;
37925       }
37926       throw 'Out of packets';
37927     };
37928   }
37929   function ResolutionLayerComponentPositionIterator(context) {
37930     var siz = context.SIZ;
37931     var tileIndex = context.currentTile.index;
37932     var tile = context.tiles[tileIndex];
37933     var layersCount = tile.codingStyleDefaultParameters.layersCount;
37934     var componentsCount = siz.Csiz;
37935     var maxDecompositionLevelsCount = 0;
37936     for (var q = 0; q < componentsCount; q++) {
37937       maxDecompositionLevelsCount = Math.max(maxDecompositionLevelsCount,
37938         tile.components[q].codingStyleParameters.decompositionLevelsCount);
37939     }
37940 
37941     var r = 0, l = 0, i = 0, k = 0;
37942 
37943     this.nextPacket = function JpxImage_nextPacket() {
37944       // Section B.12.1.2 Resolution-layer-component-position
37945       for (; r <= maxDecompositionLevelsCount; r++) {
37946         for (; l < layersCount; l++) {
37947           for (; i < componentsCount; i++) {
37948             var component = tile.components[i];
37949             if (r > component.codingStyleParameters.decompositionLevelsCount)
37950               continue;
37951 
37952             var resolution = component.resolutions[r];
37953             var numprecincts = resolution.precinctParameters.numprecincts;
37954             for (; k < numprecincts;) {
37955               var packet = createPacket(resolution, k, l);
37956               k++;
37957               return packet;
37958             }
37959             k = 0;
37960           }
37961           i = 0;
37962         }
37963         l = 0;
37964       }
37965       throw 'Out of packets';
37966     };
37967   }
37968   function buildPackets(context) {
37969     var siz = context.SIZ;
37970     var tileIndex = context.currentTile.index;
37971     var tile = context.tiles[tileIndex];
37972     var componentsCount = siz.Csiz;
37973     // Creating resolutions and sub-bands for each component
37974     for (var c = 0; c < componentsCount; c++) {
37975       var component = tile.components[c];
37976       var decompositionLevelsCount =
37977         component.codingStyleParameters.decompositionLevelsCount;
37978       // Section B.5 Resolution levels and sub-bands
37979       var resolutions = [];
37980       var subbands = [];
37981       for (var r = 0; r <= decompositionLevelsCount; r++) {
37982         var blocksDimensions = getBlocksDimensions(context, component, r);
37983         var resolution = {};
37984         var scale = 1 << (decompositionLevelsCount - r);
37985         resolution.trx0 = Math.ceil(component.tcx0 / scale);
37986         resolution.try0 = Math.ceil(component.tcy0 / scale);
37987         resolution.trx1 = Math.ceil(component.tcx1 / scale);
37988         resolution.try1 = Math.ceil(component.tcy1 / scale);
37989         buildPrecincts(context, resolution, blocksDimensions);
37990         resolutions.push(resolution);
37991 
37992         var subband;
37993         if (r === 0) {
37994           // one sub-band (LL) with last decomposition
37995           subband = {};
37996           subband.type = 'LL';
37997           subband.tbx0 = Math.ceil(component.tcx0 / scale);
37998           subband.tby0 = Math.ceil(component.tcy0 / scale);
37999           subband.tbx1 = Math.ceil(component.tcx1 / scale);
38000           subband.tby1 = Math.ceil(component.tcy1 / scale);
38001           subband.resolution = resolution;
38002           buildCodeblocks(context, subband, blocksDimensions);
38003           subbands.push(subband);
38004           resolution.subbands = [subband];
38005         } else {
38006           var bscale = 1 << (decompositionLevelsCount - r + 1);
38007           var resolutionSubbands = [];
38008           // three sub-bands (HL, LH and HH) with rest of decompositions
38009           subband = {};
38010           subband.type = 'HL';
38011           subband.tbx0 = Math.ceil(component.tcx0 / bscale - 0.5);
38012           subband.tby0 = Math.ceil(component.tcy0 / bscale);
38013           subband.tbx1 = Math.ceil(component.tcx1 / bscale - 0.5);
38014           subband.tby1 = Math.ceil(component.tcy1 / bscale);
38015           subband.resolution = resolution;
38016           buildCodeblocks(context, subband, blocksDimensions);
38017           subbands.push(subband);
38018           resolutionSubbands.push(subband);
38019 
38020           subband = {};
38021           subband.type = 'LH';
38022           subband.tbx0 = Math.ceil(component.tcx0 / bscale);
38023           subband.tby0 = Math.ceil(component.tcy0 / bscale - 0.5);
38024           subband.tbx1 = Math.ceil(component.tcx1 / bscale);
38025           subband.tby1 = Math.ceil(component.tcy1 / bscale - 0.5);
38026           subband.resolution = resolution;
38027           buildCodeblocks(context, subband, blocksDimensions);
38028           subbands.push(subband);
38029           resolutionSubbands.push(subband);
38030 
38031           subband = {};
38032           subband.type = 'HH';
38033           subband.tbx0 = Math.ceil(component.tcx0 / bscale - 0.5);
38034           subband.tby0 = Math.ceil(component.tcy0 / bscale - 0.5);
38035           subband.tbx1 = Math.ceil(component.tcx1 / bscale - 0.5);
38036           subband.tby1 = Math.ceil(component.tcy1 / bscale - 0.5);
38037           subband.resolution = resolution;
38038           buildCodeblocks(context, subband, blocksDimensions);
38039           subbands.push(subband);
38040           resolutionSubbands.push(subband);
38041 
38042           resolution.subbands = resolutionSubbands;
38043         }
38044       }
38045       component.resolutions = resolutions;
38046       component.subbands = subbands;
38047     }
38048     // Generate the packets sequence
38049     var progressionOrder = tile.codingStyleDefaultParameters.progressionOrder;
38050     var packetsIterator;
38051     switch (progressionOrder) {
38052       case 0:
38053         tile.packetsIterator =
38054           new LayerResolutionComponentPositionIterator(context);
38055         break;
38056       case 1:
38057         tile.packetsIterator =
38058           new ResolutionLayerComponentPositionIterator(context);
38059         break;
38060       default:
38061         throw 'Unsupported progression order ' + progressionOrder;
38062     }
38063   }
38064   function parseTilePackets(context, data, offset, dataLength) {
38065     var position = 0;
38066     var buffer, bufferSize = 0, skipNextBit = false;
38067     function readBits(count) {
38068       while (bufferSize < count) {
38069         var b = data[offset + position];
38070         position++;
38071         if (skipNextBit) {
38072           buffer = (buffer << 7) | b;
38073           bufferSize += 7;
38074           skipNextBit = false;
38075         } else {
38076           buffer = (buffer << 8) | b;
38077           bufferSize += 8;
38078         }
38079         if (b == 0xFF) {
38080           skipNextBit = true;
38081         }
38082       }
38083       bufferSize -= count;
38084       return (buffer >>> bufferSize) & ((1 << count) - 1);
38085     }
38086     function alignToByte() {
38087       bufferSize = 0;
38088       if (skipNextBit) {
38089         position++;
38090         skipNextBit = false;
38091       }
38092     }
38093     function readCodingpasses() {
38094       var value = readBits(1);
38095       if (value === 0)
38096         return 1;
38097       value = (value << 1) | readBits(1);
38098       if (value == 0x02)
38099         return 2;
38100       value = (value << 2) | readBits(2);
38101       if (value <= 0x0E)
38102         return (value & 0x03) + 3;
38103       value = (value << 5) | readBits(5);
38104       if (value <= 0x1FE)
38105         return (value & 0x1F) + 6;
38106       value = (value << 7) | readBits(7);
38107       return (value & 0x7F) + 37;
38108     }
38109     var tileIndex = context.currentTile.index;
38110     var tile = context.tiles[tileIndex];
38111     var packetsIterator = tile.packetsIterator;
38112     while (position < dataLength) {
38113       var packet = packetsIterator.nextPacket();
38114       if (!readBits(1)) {
38115         alignToByte();
38116         continue;
38117       }
38118       var layerNumber = packet.layerNumber;
38119       var queue = [];
38120       for (var i = 0, ii = packet.codeblocks.length; i < ii; i++) {
38121         var codeblock = packet.codeblocks[i];
38122         var precinct = codeblock.precinct;
38123         var codeblockColumn = codeblock.cbx - precinct.cbxMin;
38124         var codeblockRow = codeblock.cby - precinct.cbyMin;
38125         var codeblockIncluded = false;
38126         var firstTimeInclusion = false;
38127         if ('included' in codeblock) {
38128           codeblockIncluded = !!readBits(1);
38129         } else {
38130           // reading inclusion tree
38131           var precinct = codeblock.precinct;
38132           var inclusionTree, zeroBitPlanesTree;
38133           if ('inclusionTree' in precinct) {
38134             inclusionTree = precinct.inclusionTree;
38135           } else {
38136             // building inclusion and zero bit-planes trees
38137             var width = precinct.cbxMax - precinct.cbxMin + 1;
38138             var height = precinct.cbyMax - precinct.cbyMin + 1;
38139             inclusionTree = new InclusionTree(width, height, layerNumber);
38140             zeroBitPlanesTree = new TagTree(width, height);
38141             precinct.inclusionTree = inclusionTree;
38142             precinct.zeroBitPlanesTree = zeroBitPlanesTree;
38143           }
38144 
38145           if (inclusionTree.reset(codeblockColumn, codeblockRow, layerNumber)) {
38146             while (true) {
38147               if (readBits(1)) {
38148                 var valueReady = !inclusionTree.nextLevel();
38149                 if (valueReady) {
38150                   codeblock.included = true;
38151                   codeblockIncluded = firstTimeInclusion = true;
38152                   break;
38153                 }
38154               } else {
38155                 inclusionTree.incrementValue(layerNumber);
38156                 break;
38157               }
38158             }
38159           }
38160         }
38161         if (!codeblockIncluded)
38162           continue;
38163         if (firstTimeInclusion) {
38164           zeroBitPlanesTree = precinct.zeroBitPlanesTree;
38165           zeroBitPlanesTree.reset(codeblockColumn, codeblockRow);
38166           while (true) {
38167             if (readBits(1)) {
38168               var valueReady = !zeroBitPlanesTree.nextLevel();
38169               if (valueReady)
38170                 break;
38171             } else
38172               zeroBitPlanesTree.incrementValue();
38173           }
38174           codeblock.zeroBitPlanes = zeroBitPlanesTree.value;
38175         }
38176         var codingpasses = readCodingpasses();
38177         while (readBits(1))
38178           codeblock.Lblock++;
38179         var codingpassesLog2 = log2(codingpasses);
38180         // rounding down log2
38181         var bits = ((codingpasses < (1 << codingpassesLog2)) ?
38182           codingpassesLog2 - 1 : codingpassesLog2) + codeblock.Lblock;
38183         var codedDataLength = readBits(bits);
38184         queue.push({
38185           codeblock: codeblock,
38186           codingpasses: codingpasses,
38187           dataLength: codedDataLength
38188         });
38189       }
38190       alignToByte();
38191       while (queue.length > 0) {
38192         var packetItem = queue.shift();
38193         var codeblock = packetItem.codeblock;
38194         if (!('data' in codeblock))
38195           codeblock.data = [];
38196         codeblock.data.push({
38197           data: data,
38198           start: offset + position,
38199           end: offset + position + packetItem.dataLength,
38200           codingpasses: packetItem.codingpasses
38201         });
38202         position += packetItem.dataLength;
38203       }
38204     }
38205     return position;
38206   }
38207   function copyCoefficients(coefficients, x0, y0, width, height,
38208                             delta, mb, codeblocks, transformation,
38209                             segmentationSymbolUsed) {
38210     var r = 0.5; // formula (E-6)
38211     for (var i = 0, ii = codeblocks.length; i < ii; ++i) {
38212       var codeblock = codeblocks[i];
38213       var blockWidth = codeblock.tbx1_ - codeblock.tbx0_;
38214       var blockHeight = codeblock.tby1_ - codeblock.tby0_;
38215       if (blockWidth === 0 || blockHeight === 0)
38216         continue;
38217       if (!('data' in codeblock))
38218         continue;
38219 
38220       var bitModel, currentCodingpassType;
38221       bitModel = new BitModel(blockWidth, blockHeight, codeblock.subbandType,
38222         codeblock.zeroBitPlanes);
38223       currentCodingpassType = 2; // first bit plane starts from cleanup
38224 
38225       // collect data
38226       var data = codeblock.data, totalLength = 0, codingpasses = 0;
38227       for (var q = 0, qq = data.length; q < qq; q++) {
38228         var dataItem = data[q];
38229         totalLength += dataItem.end - dataItem.start;
38230         codingpasses += dataItem.codingpasses;
38231       }
38232       var encodedData = new Uint8Array(totalLength), k = 0;
38233       for (var q = 0, qq = data.length; q < qq; q++) {
38234         var dataItem = data[q];
38235         var chunk = dataItem.data.subarray(dataItem.start, dataItem.end);
38236         encodedData.set(chunk, k);
38237         k += chunk.length;
38238       }
38239       // decoding the item
38240       var decoder = new ArithmeticDecoder(encodedData, 0, totalLength);
38241       bitModel.setDecoder(decoder);
38242 
38243       for (var q = 0; q < codingpasses; q++) {
38244         switch (currentCodingpassType) {
38245           case 0:
38246             bitModel.runSignificancePropogationPass();
38247             break;
38248           case 1:
38249             bitModel.runMagnitudeRefinementPass();
38250             break;
38251           case 2:
38252             bitModel.runCleanupPass();
38253             if (segmentationSymbolUsed)
38254               bitModel.checkSegmentationSymbol();
38255             break;
38256         }
38257         currentCodingpassType = (currentCodingpassType + 1) % 3;
38258       }
38259 
38260       var offset = (codeblock.tbx0_ - x0) + (codeblock.tby0_ - y0) * width;
38261       var position = 0;
38262       for (var j = 0; j < blockHeight; j++) {
38263         for (var k = 0; k < blockWidth; k++) {
38264           var n = (bitModel.coefficentsSign[position] ? -1 : 1) *
38265             bitModel.coefficentsMagnitude[position];
38266           var nb = bitModel.bitsDecoded[position], correction;
38267           if (transformation === 0 || mb > nb) {
38268             // use r only if transformation is irreversible or
38269             // not all bitplanes were decoded for reversible transformation
38270             n += n < 0 ? n - r : n > 0 ? n + r : 0;
38271             correction = 1 << (mb - nb);
38272           } else
38273             correction = 1;
38274           coefficients[offset++] = n * correction * delta;
38275           position++;
38276         }
38277         offset += width - blockWidth;
38278       }
38279     }
38280   }
38281   function transformTile(context, tile, c) {
38282     var component = tile.components[c];
38283     var codingStyleParameters = component.codingStyleParameters;
38284     var quantizationParameters = component.quantizationParameters;
38285     var decompositionLevelsCount =
38286       codingStyleParameters.decompositionLevelsCount;
38287     var spqcds = quantizationParameters.SPqcds;
38288     var scalarExpounded = quantizationParameters.scalarExpounded;
38289     var guardBits = quantizationParameters.guardBits;
38290     var transformation = codingStyleParameters.transformation;
38291     var segmentationSymbolUsed = codingStyleParameters.segmentationSymbolUsed;
38292     var precision = context.components[c].precision;
38293 
38294     var subbandCoefficients = [];
38295     var k = 0, b = 0;
38296     for (var i = 0; i <= decompositionLevelsCount; i++) {
38297       var resolution = component.resolutions[i];
38298 
38299       for (var j = 0, jj = resolution.subbands.length; j < jj; j++) {
38300         var mu, epsilon;
38301         if (!scalarExpounded) {
38302           // formula E-5
38303           mu = spqcds[0].mu;
38304           epsilon = spqcds[0].epsilon + (i > 0 ? 1 - i : 0);
38305         } else {
38306           mu = spqcds[b].mu;
38307           epsilon = spqcds[b].epsilon;
38308         }
38309 
38310         var subband = resolution.subbands[j];
38311         var width = subband.tbx1 - subband.tbx0;
38312         var height = subband.tby1 - subband.tby0;
38313         var gainLog2 = SubbandsGainLog2[subband.type];
38314 
38315         // calulate quantization coefficient (Section E.1.1.1)
38316         var delta = Math.pow(2, (precision + gainLog2) - epsilon) *
38317           (1 + mu / 2048);
38318         var mb = (guardBits + epsilon - 1);
38319 
38320         var coefficients = new Float32Array(width * height);
38321         copyCoefficients(coefficients, subband.tbx0, subband.tby0,
38322           width, height, delta, mb, subband.codeblocks, transformation,
38323           segmentationSymbolUsed);
38324 
38325         subbandCoefficients.push({
38326           width: width,
38327           height: height,
38328           items: coefficients
38329         });
38330 
38331         b++;
38332       }
38333     }
38334 
38335     var transformation = codingStyleParameters.transformation;
38336     var transform = transformation === 0 ? new IrreversibleTransform() :
38337       new ReversibleTransform();
38338     var result = transform.calculate(subbandCoefficients,
38339       component.tcx0, component.tcy0);
38340     return {
38341       left: component.tcx0,
38342       top: component.tcy0,
38343       width: result.width,
38344       height: result.height,
38345       items: result.items
38346     };
38347   }
38348   function transformComponents(context) {
38349     var siz = context.SIZ;
38350     var components = context.components;
38351     var componentsCount = siz.Csiz;
38352     var resultImages = [];
38353     for (var i = 0, ii = context.tiles.length; i < ii; i++) {
38354       var tile = context.tiles[i];
38355       var result = [];
38356       for (var c = 0; c < componentsCount; c++) {
38357         var image = transformTile(context, tile, c);
38358         result.push(image);
38359       }
38360 
38361       // Section G.2.2 Inverse multi component transform
38362       if (tile.codingStyleDefaultParameters.multipleComponentTransform) {
38363         var y0items = result[0].items;
38364         var y1items = result[1].items;
38365         var y2items = result[2].items;
38366         for (var j = 0, jj = y0items.length; j < jj; j++) {
38367           var y0 = y0items[j], y1 = y1items[j], y2 = y2items[j];
38368           var i1 = y0 - ((y2 + y1) >> 2);
38369           y1items[j] = i1;
38370           y0items[j] = y2 + i1;
38371           y2items[j] = y1 + i1;
38372         }
38373       }
38374 
38375       // Section G.1 DC level shifting to unsigned component values
38376       for (var c = 0; c < componentsCount; c++) {
38377         var component = components[c];
38378         if (component.isSigned)
38379           continue;
38380 
38381         var offset = 1 << (component.precision - 1);
38382         var tileImage = result[c];
38383         var items = tileImage.items;
38384         for (var j = 0, jj = items.length; j < jj; j++)
38385           items[j] += offset;
38386       }
38387 
38388       // To simplify things: shift and clamp output to 8 bit unsigned
38389       for (var c = 0; c < componentsCount; c++) {
38390         var component = components[c];
38391         var offset = component.isSigned ? 128 : 0;
38392         var shift = component.precision - 8;
38393         var tileImage = result[c];
38394         var items = tileImage.items;
38395         var data = new Uint8Array(items.length);
38396         for (var j = 0, jj = items.length; j < jj; j++) {
38397           var value = (items[j] >> shift) + offset;
38398           data[j] = value < 0 ? 0 : value > 255 ? 255 : value;
38399         }
38400         result[c].items = data;
38401       }
38402 
38403       resultImages.push(result);
38404     }
38405     return resultImages;
38406   }
38407   function initializeTile(context, tileIndex) {
38408     var siz = context.SIZ;
38409     var componentsCount = siz.Csiz;
38410     var tile = context.tiles[tileIndex];
38411     var resultTiles = [];
38412     for (var c = 0; c < componentsCount; c++) {
38413       var component = tile.components[c];
38414       var qcdOrQcc = c in context.currentTile.QCC ?
38415         context.currentTile.QCC[c] : context.currentTile.QCD;
38416       component.quantizationParameters = qcdOrQcc;
38417       var codOrCoc = c in context.currentTile.COC ?
38418         context.currentTile.COC[c] : context.currentTile.COD;
38419       component.codingStyleParameters = codOrCoc;
38420     }
38421     tile.codingStyleDefaultParameters = context.currentTile.COD;
38422   }
38423 
38424   // Section B.10.2 Tag trees
38425   var TagTree = (function TagTreeClosure() {
38426     function TagTree(width, height) {
38427       var levelsLength = log2(Math.max(width, height)) + 1;
38428       this.levels = [];
38429       for (var i = 0; i < levelsLength; i++) {
38430         var level = {
38431           width: width,
38432           height: height,
38433           items: []
38434         };
38435         this.levels.push(level);
38436         width = Math.ceil(width / 2);
38437         height = Math.ceil(height / 2);
38438       }
38439     }
38440     TagTree.prototype = {
38441       reset: function TagTree_reset(i, j) {
38442         var currentLevel = 0, value = 0;
38443         while (currentLevel < this.levels.length) {
38444           var level = this.levels[currentLevel];
38445           var index = i + j * level.width;
38446           if (index in level.items) {
38447             value = level.items[index];
38448             break;
38449           }
38450           level.index = index;
38451           i >>= 1;
38452           j >>= 1;
38453           currentLevel++;
38454         }
38455         currentLevel--;
38456         var level = this.levels[currentLevel];
38457         level.items[level.index] = value;
38458         this.currentLevel = currentLevel;
38459         delete this.value;
38460       },
38461       incrementValue: function TagTree_incrementValue() {
38462         var level = this.levels[this.currentLevel];
38463         level.items[level.index]++;
38464       },
38465       nextLevel: function TagTree_nextLevel() {
38466         var currentLevel = this.currentLevel;
38467         var level = this.levels[currentLevel];
38468         var value = level.items[level.index];
38469         currentLevel--;
38470         if (currentLevel < 0) {
38471           this.value = value;
38472           return false;
38473         }
38474 
38475         this.currentLevel = currentLevel;
38476         var level = this.levels[currentLevel];
38477         level.items[level.index] = value;
38478         return true;
38479       }
38480     };
38481     return TagTree;
38482   })();
38483 
38484   var InclusionTree = (function InclusionTreeClosure() {
38485     function InclusionTree(width, height,  defaultValue) {
38486       var levelsLength = log2(Math.max(width, height)) + 1;
38487       this.levels = [];
38488       for (var i = 0; i < levelsLength; i++) {
38489         var items = new Uint8Array(width * height);
38490         for (var j = 0, jj = items.length; j < jj; j++)
38491           items[j] = defaultValue;
38492 
38493         var level = {
38494           width: width,
38495           height: height,
38496           items: items
38497         };
38498         this.levels.push(level);
38499 
38500         width = Math.ceil(width / 2);
38501         height = Math.ceil(height / 2);
38502       }
38503     }
38504     InclusionTree.prototype = {
38505       reset: function InclusionTree_reset(i, j, stopValue) {
38506         var currentLevel = 0;
38507         while (currentLevel < this.levels.length) {
38508           var level = this.levels[currentLevel];
38509           var index = i + j * level.width;
38510           level.index = index;
38511           var value = level.items[index];
38512 
38513           if (value == 0xFF)
38514             break;
38515 
38516           if (value > stopValue) {
38517             this.currentLevel = currentLevel;
38518             // already know about this one, propagating the value to top levels
38519             this.propagateValues();
38520             return false;
38521           }
38522 
38523           i >>= 1;
38524           j >>= 1;
38525           currentLevel++;
38526         }
38527         this.currentLevel = currentLevel - 1;
38528         return true;
38529       },
38530       incrementValue: function InclusionTree_incrementValue(stopValue) {
38531         var level = this.levels[this.currentLevel];
38532         level.items[level.index] = stopValue + 1;
38533         this.propagateValues();
38534       },
38535       propagateValues: function InclusionTree_propagateValues() {
38536         var levelIndex = this.currentLevel;
38537         var level = this.levels[levelIndex];
38538         var currentValue = level.items[level.index];
38539         while (--levelIndex >= 0) {
38540           var level = this.levels[levelIndex];
38541           level.items[level.index] = currentValue;
38542         }
38543       },
38544       nextLevel: function InclusionTree_nextLevel() {
38545         var currentLevel = this.currentLevel;
38546         var level = this.levels[currentLevel];
38547         var value = level.items[level.index];
38548         level.items[level.index] = 0xFF;
38549         currentLevel--;
38550         if (currentLevel < 0)
38551           return false;
38552 
38553         this.currentLevel = currentLevel;
38554         var level = this.levels[currentLevel];
38555         level.items[level.index] = value;
38556         return true;
38557       }
38558     };
38559     return InclusionTree;
38560   })();

38614     function ArithmeticDecoder(data, start, end) {
38615       this.data = data;
38616       this.bp = start;
38617       this.dataEnd = end;
38618 
38619       this.chigh = data[start];
38620       this.clow = 0;
38621 
38622       this.byteIn();
38623 
38624       this.chigh = ((this.chigh << 7) & 0xFFFF) | ((this.clow >> 9) & 0x7F);
38625       this.clow = (this.clow << 7) & 0xFFFF;
38626       this.ct -= 7;
38627       this.a = 0x8000;
38628     }
38629 
38630     ArithmeticDecoder.prototype = {
38631       byteIn: function ArithmeticDecoder_byteIn() {
38632         var data = this.data;
38633         var bp = this.bp;
38634         if (data[bp] == 0xFF) {
38635           var b1 = data[bp + 1];
38636           if (b1 > 0x8F) {
38637             this.clow += 0xFF00;
38638             this.ct = 8;
38639           } else {
38640             bp++;
38641             this.clow += (data[bp] << 9);
38642             this.ct = 7;
38643             this.bp = bp;
38644           }
38645         } else {
38646           bp++;
38647           this.clow += bp < this.dataEnd ? (data[bp] << 8) : 0xFF00;
38648           this.ct = 8;
38649           this.bp = bp;
38650         }
38651         if (this.clow > 0xFFFF) {
38652           this.chigh += (this.clow >> 16);
38653           this.clow &= 0xFFFF;
38654         }
38655       },
38656       readBit: function ArithmeticDecoder_readBit(cx) {
38657         var qeIcx = QeTable[cx.index].qe;
38658         this.a -= qeIcx;
38659 
38660         if (this.chigh < qeIcx) {
38661           var d = this.exchangeLps(cx);
38662           this.renormD();
38663           return d;
38664         } else {
38665           this.chigh -= qeIcx;
38666           if ((this.a & 0x8000) === 0) {
38667             var d = this.exchangeMps(cx);
38668             this.renormD();
38669             return d;
38670           } else {
38671             return cx.mps;
38672           }
38673         }
38674       },
38675       renormD: function ArithmeticDecoder_renormD() {
38676         do {
38677           if (this.ct === 0)
38678             this.byteIn();
38679 
38680           this.a <<= 1;
38681           this.chigh = ((this.chigh << 1) & 0xFFFF) | ((this.clow >> 15) & 1);
38682           this.clow = (this.clow << 1) & 0xFFFF;
38683           this.ct--;
38684         } while ((this.a & 0x8000) === 0);
38685       },
38686       exchangeMps: function ArithmeticDecoder_exchangeMps(cx) {
38687         var d;
38688         var qeTableIcx = QeTable[cx.index];
38689         if (this.a < qeTableIcx.qe) {
38690           d = 1 - cx.mps;
38691 
38692           if (qeTableIcx.switchFlag == 1) {
38693             cx.mps = 1 - cx.mps;
38694           }
38695           cx.index = qeTableIcx.nlps;
38696         } else {
38697           d = cx.mps;
38698           cx.index = qeTableIcx.nmps;
38699         }
38700         return d;
38701       },
38702       exchangeLps: function ArithmeticDecoder_exchangeLps(cx) {
38703         var d;
38704         var qeTableIcx = QeTable[cx.index];
38705         if (this.a < qeTableIcx.qe) {
38706           this.a = qeTableIcx.qe;
38707           d = cx.mps;
38708           cx.index = qeTableIcx.nmps;
38709         } else {
38710           this.a = qeTableIcx.qe;
38711           d = 1 - cx.mps;
38712 
38713           if (qeTableIcx.switchFlag == 1) {
38714             cx.mps = 1 - cx.mps;
38715           }
38716           cx.index = qeTableIcx.nlps;
38717         }
38718         return d;
38719       }
38720     };
38721 
38722     return ArithmeticDecoder;
38723   })();

38725   // Section D. Coefficient bit modeling
38726   var BitModel = (function BitModelClosure() {
38727     // Table D-1
38728     // The index is binary presentation: 0dddvvhh, ddd - sum of Di (0..4),
38729     // vv - sum of Vi (0..2), and hh - sum of Hi (0..2)
38730     var LLAndLHContextsLabel = new Uint8Array([
38731       0, 5, 8, 0, 3, 7, 8, 0, 4, 7, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, 8, 0, 3, 7, 8, 0, 4,
38732       7, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 6, 8, 0, 3, 7, 8, 0, 4, 7, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 6,
38733       8, 0, 3, 7, 8, 0, 4, 7, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 6, 8, 0, 3, 7, 8, 0, 4, 7, 8
38734     ]);
38735     var HLContextLabel = new Uint8Array([
38736       0, 3, 4, 0, 5, 7, 7, 0, 8, 8, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 3, 4, 0, 6, 7, 7, 0, 8,
38737       8, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 3, 4, 0, 6, 7, 7, 0, 8, 8, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 3,
38738       4, 0, 6, 7, 7, 0, 8, 8, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 2, 3, 4, 0, 6, 7, 7, 0, 8, 8, 8
38739     ]);
38740     var HHContextLabel = new Uint8Array([
38741       0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 2, 2, 0, 2, 2, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 3, 4, 5, 0, 4, 5, 5, 0, 5,
38742       5, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 6, 7, 7, 0, 7, 7, 7, 0, 7, 7, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 8, 8,
38743       8, 0, 8, 8, 8, 0, 8, 8, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 8, 8, 8, 0, 8, 8, 8, 0, 8, 8, 8
38744     ]);
38745 
38746     // Table D-2
38747     function calcSignContribution(significance0, sign0, significance1, sign1) {
38748       if (significance1) {
38749         if (!sign1)
38750           return significance0 ? (!sign0 ? 1 : 0) : 1;
38751         else
38752           return significance0 ? (!sign0 ? 0 : -1) : -1;
38753       } else
38754         return significance0 ? (!sign0 ? 1 : -1) : 0;
38755     }
38756     // Table D-3
38757     var SignContextLabels = [
38758       {contextLabel: 13, xorBit: 0},
38759       {contextLabel: 12, xorBit: 0},
38760       {contextLabel: 11, xorBit: 0},
38761       {contextLabel: 10, xorBit: 0},
38762       {contextLabel: 9, xorBit: 0},
38763       {contextLabel: 10, xorBit: 1},
38764       {contextLabel: 11, xorBit: 1},
38765       {contextLabel: 12, xorBit: 1},
38766       {contextLabel: 13, xorBit: 1}
38767     ];
38768 
38769     function BitModel(width, height, subband, zeroBitPlanes) {
38770       this.width = width;
38771       this.height = height;
38772 
38773       this.contextLabelTable = subband == 'HH' ? HHContextLabel :
38774         subband == 'HL' ? HLContextLabel : LLAndLHContextsLabel;
38775 
38776       var coefficientCount = width * height;
38777 
38778       // coefficients outside the encoding region treated as insignificant
38779       // add border state cells for significanceState
38780       this.neighborsSignificance = new Uint8Array(coefficientCount);
38781       this.coefficentsSign = new Uint8Array(coefficientCount);
38782       this.coefficentsMagnitude = new Uint32Array(coefficientCount);
38783       this.processingFlags = new Uint8Array(coefficientCount);
38784 
38785       var bitsDecoded = new Uint8Array(this.width * this.height);
38786       for (var i = 0, ii = bitsDecoded.length; i < ii; i++)
38787         bitsDecoded[i] = zeroBitPlanes;
38788       this.bitsDecoded = bitsDecoded;
38789 
38790       this.reset();
38791     }
38792 
38793     BitModel.prototype = {
38794       setDecoder: function BitModel_setDecoder(decoder) {
38795         this.decoder = decoder;
38796       },
38797       reset: function BitModel_reset() {
38798         this.uniformContext = {index: 46, mps: 0};
38799         this.runLengthContext = {index: 3, mps: 0};
38800         this.contexts = [];
38801         this.contexts.push({index: 4, mps: 0});
38802         for (var i = 1; i <= 16; i++)
38803           this.contexts.push({index: 0, mps: 0});
38804       },
38805       setNeighborsSignificance:
38806         function BitModel_setNeighborsSignificance(row, column) {
38807         var neighborsSignificance = this.neighborsSignificance;
38808         var width = this.width, height = this.height;
38809         var index = row * width + column;
38810         if (row > 0) {
38811           if (column > 0)
38812             neighborsSignificance[index - width - 1] += 0x10;
38813           if (column + 1 < width)
38814             neighborsSignificance[index - width + 1] += 0x10;
38815           neighborsSignificance[index - width] += 0x04;
38816         }
38817         if (row + 1 < height) {
38818           if (column > 0)
38819             neighborsSignificance[index + width - 1] += 0x10;
38820           if (column + 1 < width)
38821             neighborsSignificance[index + width + 1] += 0x10;
38822           neighborsSignificance[index + width] += 0x04;
38823         }
38824         if (column > 0)
38825           neighborsSignificance[index - 1] += 0x01;
38826         if (column + 1 < width)
38827           neighborsSignificance[index + 1] += 0x01;
38828         neighborsSignificance[index] |= 0x80;
38829       },
38830       runSignificancePropogationPass:
38831         function BitModel_runSignificancePropogationPass() {
38832         var decoder = this.decoder;
38833         var width = this.width, height = this.height;
38834         var coefficentsMagnitude = this.coefficentsMagnitude;
38835         var coefficentsSign = this.coefficentsSign;
38836         var contextLabels = this.contextLabels;
38837         var neighborsSignificance = this.neighborsSignificance;
38838         var processingFlags = this.processingFlags;
38839         var contexts = this.contexts;
38840         var labels = this.contextLabelTable;
38841         var bitsDecoded = this.bitsDecoded;
38842         // clear processed flag
38843         var processedInverseMask = ~1;
38844         var processedMask = 1;
38845         var firstMagnitudeBitMask = 2;
38846         for (var q = 0, qq = width * height; q < qq; q++)
38847           processingFlags[q] &= processedInverseMask;
38848 
38849         for (var i0 = 0; i0 < height; i0 += 4) {
38850           for (var j = 0; j < width; j++) {
38851             var index = i0 * width + j;
38852             for (var i1 = 0; i1 < 4; i1++, index += width) {
38853               var i = i0 + i1;
38854               if (i >= height)
38855                 break;
38856 
38857               if (coefficentsMagnitude[index] || !neighborsSignificance[index])
38858                 continue;
38859 
38860               var contextLabel = labels[neighborsSignificance[index]];
38861               var cx = contexts[contextLabel];
38862               var decision = decoder.readBit(cx);
38863               if (decision) {
38864                 var sign = this.decodeSignBit(i, j);
38865                 coefficentsSign[index] = sign;
38866                 coefficentsMagnitude[index] = 1;
38867                 this.setNeighborsSignificance(i, j);
38868                 processingFlags[index] |= firstMagnitudeBitMask;
38869               }
38870               bitsDecoded[index]++;
38871               processingFlags[index] |= processedMask;
38872             }
38873           }
38874         }
38875       },
38876       decodeSignBit: function BitModel_decodeSignBit(row, column) {
38877         var width = this.width, height = this.height;
38878         var index = row * width + column;
38879         var coefficentsMagnitude = this.coefficentsMagnitude;
38880         var coefficentsSign = this.coefficentsSign;
38881         var horizontalContribution = calcSignContribution(
38882           column > 0 && coefficentsMagnitude[index - 1],
38883           coefficentsSign[index - 1],
38884           column + 1 < width && coefficentsMagnitude[index + 1],
38885           coefficentsSign[index + 1]);
38886         var verticalContribution = calcSignContribution(
38887           row > 0 && coefficentsMagnitude[index - width],
38888           coefficentsSign[index - width],
38889           row + 1 < height && coefficentsMagnitude[index + width],
38890           coefficentsSign[index + width]);
38891 
38892         var contextLabelAndXor = SignContextLabels[
38893           3 * (1 - horizontalContribution) + (1 - verticalContribution)];
38894         var contextLabel = contextLabelAndXor.contextLabel;
38895         var cx = this.contexts[contextLabel];
38896         var decoded = this.decoder.readBit(cx);
38897         return decoded ^ contextLabelAndXor.xorBit;
38898       },
38899       runMagnitudeRefinementPass:
38900         function BitModel_runMagnitudeRefinementPass() {
38901         var decoder = this.decoder;
38902         var width = this.width, height = this.height;
38903         var coefficentsMagnitude = this.coefficentsMagnitude;
38904         var neighborsSignificance = this.neighborsSignificance;
38905         var contexts = this.contexts;
38906         var bitsDecoded = this.bitsDecoded;
38907         var processingFlags = this.processingFlags;
38908         var processedMask = 1;
38909         var firstMagnitudeBitMask = 2;
38910         for (var i0 = 0; i0 < height; i0 += 4) {
38911           for (var j = 0; j < width; j++) {
38912             for (var i1 = 0; i1 < 4; i1++) {
38913               var i = i0 + i1;
38914               if (i >= height)
38915                 break;
38916               var index = i * width + j;
38917 
38918               // significant but not those that have just become
38919               if (!coefficentsMagnitude[index] ||
38920                 (processingFlags[index] & processedMask) !== 0)
38921                 continue;
38922 
38923               var contextLabel = 16;
38924               if ((processingFlags[index] &
38925                 firstMagnitudeBitMask) !== 0) {
38926                 processingFlags[i * width + j] ^= firstMagnitudeBitMask;
38927                 // first refinement
38928                 var significance = neighborsSignificance[index];
38929                 var sumOfSignificance = (significance & 3) +
38930                   ((significance >> 2) & 3) + ((significance >> 4) & 7);
38931                 contextLabel = sumOfSignificance >= 1 ? 15 : 14;
38932               }
38933 
38934               var cx = contexts[contextLabel];
38935               var bit = decoder.readBit(cx);
38936               coefficentsMagnitude[index] =
38937                 (coefficentsMagnitude[index] << 1) | bit;
38938               bitsDecoded[index]++;
38939               processingFlags[index] |= processedMask;
38940             }
38941           }
38942         }
38943       },
38944       runCleanupPass: function BitModel_runCleanupPass() {
38945         var decoder = this.decoder;
38946         var width = this.width, height = this.height;
38947         var neighborsSignificance = this.neighborsSignificance;
38948         var significanceState = this.significanceState;
38949         var coefficentsMagnitude = this.coefficentsMagnitude;
38950         var coefficentsSign = this.coefficentsSign;
38951         var contexts = this.contexts;
38952         var labels = this.contextLabelTable;
38953         var bitsDecoded = this.bitsDecoded;
38954         var processingFlags = this.processingFlags;
38955         var processedMask = 1;
38956         var firstMagnitudeBitMask = 2;
38957         var oneRowDown = width;
38958         var twoRowsDown = width * 2;
38959         var threeRowsDown = width * 3;
38960         for (var i0 = 0; i0 < height; i0 += 4) {
38961           for (var j = 0; j < width; j++) {
38962             var index0 = i0 * width + j;
38963             // using the property: labels[neighborsSignificance[index]] == 0
38964             // when neighborsSignificance[index] == 0
38965             var allEmpty = i0 + 3 < height &&
38966               processingFlags[index0] === 0 &&
38967               processingFlags[index0 + oneRowDown] === 0 &&
38968               processingFlags[index0 + twoRowsDown] === 0 &&
38969               processingFlags[index0 + threeRowsDown] === 0 &&
38970               neighborsSignificance[index0] === 0 &&
38971               neighborsSignificance[index0 + oneRowDown] === 0 &&
38972               neighborsSignificance[index0 + twoRowsDown] === 0 &&
38973               neighborsSignificance[index0 + threeRowsDown] === 0;
38974             var i1 = 0, index = index0;
38975             var cx, i;
38976             if (allEmpty) {
38977               cx = this.runLengthContext;
38978               var hasSignificantCoefficent = decoder.readBit(cx);
38979               if (!hasSignificantCoefficent) {
38980                 bitsDecoded[index0]++;
38981                 bitsDecoded[index0 + oneRowDown]++;
38982                 bitsDecoded[index0 + twoRowsDown]++;
38983                 bitsDecoded[index0 + threeRowsDown]++;
38984                 continue; // next column
38985               }
38986               cx = this.uniformContext;
38987               i1 = (decoder.readBit(cx) << 1) | decoder.readBit(cx);
38988               i = i0 + i1;
38989               index += i1 * width;
38990 
38991               var sign = this.decodeSignBit(i, j);
38992               coefficentsSign[index] = sign;
38993               coefficentsMagnitude[index] = 1;
38994               this.setNeighborsSignificance(i, j);
38995               processingFlags[index] |= firstMagnitudeBitMask;
38996 
38997               index = index0;
38998               for (var i2 = i0; i2 <= i; i2++, index += width)
38999                 bitsDecoded[index]++;
39000 
39001               i1++;
39002             }
39003             for (; i1 < 4; i1++, index += width) {
39004               i = i0 + i1;
39005               if (i >= height)
39006                 break;
39007 
39008               if (coefficentsMagnitude[index] ||
39009                 (processingFlags[index] & processedMask) !== 0)
39010                 continue;
39011 
39012               var contextLabel = labels[neighborsSignificance[index]];
39013               cx = contexts[contextLabel];
39014               var decision = decoder.readBit(cx);
39015               if (decision == 1) {
39016                 var sign = this.decodeSignBit(i, j);
39017                 coefficentsSign[index] = sign;
39018                 coefficentsMagnitude[index] = 1;
39019                 this.setNeighborsSignificance(i, j);
39020                 processingFlags[index] |= firstMagnitudeBitMask;
39021               }
39022               bitsDecoded[index]++;
39023             }
39024           }
39025         }
39026       },
39027       checkSegmentationSymbol: function BitModel_checkSegmentationSymbol() {
39028         var decoder = this.decoder;
39029         var cx = this.uniformContext;
39030         var symbol = (decoder.readBit(cx) << 3) | (decoder.readBit(cx) << 2) |
39031                      (decoder.readBit(cx) << 1) | decoder.readBit(cx);
39032         if (symbol != 0xA)
39033           throw 'Invalid segmentation symbol';
39034       }
39035     };
39036 
39037     return BitModel;
39038   })();

39041   var Transform = (function TransformClosure() {
39042     function Transform() {
39043     }
39044     Transform.prototype.calculate =
39045       function transformCalculate(subbands, u0, v0) {
39046       var ll = subbands[0];
39047       for (var i = 1, ii = subbands.length, j = 1; i < ii; i += 3, j++) {
39048         ll = this.iterate(ll, subbands[i], subbands[i + 1],
39049                           subbands[i + 2], u0, v0);
39050       }
39051       return ll;
39052     };
39053     Transform.prototype.iterate = function Transform_iterate(ll, hl, lh, hh,
39054                                                             u0, v0) {
39055       var llWidth = ll.width, llHeight = ll.height, llItems = ll.items;
39056       var hlWidth = hl.width, hlHeight = hl.height, hlItems = hl.items;
39057       var lhWidth = lh.width, lhHeight = lh.height, lhItems = lh.items;
39058       var hhWidth = hh.width, hhHeight = hh.height, hhItems = hh.items;
39059 
39060       // Section F.3.3 interleave
39061       var width = llWidth + hlWidth;
39062       var height = llHeight + lhHeight;
39063       var items = new Float32Array(width * height);
39064       for (var i = 0, ii = llHeight; i < ii; i++) {
39065         var k = i * llWidth, l = i * 2 * width;
39066         for (var j = 0, jj = llWidth; j < jj; j++, k++, l += 2)
39067           items[l] = llItems[k];
39068       }
39069       for (var i = 0, ii = hlHeight; i < ii; i++) {
39070         var k = i * hlWidth, l = i * 2 * width + 1;
39071         for (var j = 0, jj = hlWidth; j < jj; j++, k++, l += 2)
39072           items[l] = hlItems[k];
39073       }
39074       for (var i = 0, ii = lhHeight; i < ii; i++) {
39075         var k = i * lhWidth, l = (i * 2 + 1) * width;
39076         for (var j = 0, jj = lhWidth; j < jj; j++, k++, l += 2)
39077           items[l] = lhItems[k];
39078       }
39079       for (var i = 0, ii = hhHeight; i < ii; i++) {
39080         var k = i * hhWidth, l = (i * 2 + 1) * width + 1;
39081         for (var j = 0, jj = hhWidth; j < jj; j++, k++, l += 2)
39082           items[l] = hhItems[k];
39083       }
39084 
39085       var bufferPadding = 4;
39086       var bufferLength = new Float32Array(Math.max(width, height) +
39087         2 * bufferPadding);
39088       var buffer = new Float32Array(bufferLength);
39089       var bufferOut = new Float32Array(bufferLength);
39090 
39091       // Section F.3.4 HOR_SR
39092       for (var v = 0; v < height; v++) {
39093         if (width == 1) {
39094           // if width = 1, when u0 even keep items as is, when odd divide by 2
39095           if ((u0 % 1) !== 0) {
39096             items[v * width] /= 2;
39097           }
39098           continue;
39099         }
39100 
39101         var k = v * width;
39102         var l = bufferPadding;
39103         for (var u = 0; u < width; u++, k++, l++)
39104           buffer[l] = items[k];
39105 
39106         // Section F.3.7 extending... using max extension of 4
39107         var i1 = bufferPadding - 1, j1 = bufferPadding + 1;
39108         var i2 = bufferPadding + width - 2, j2 = bufferPadding + width;
39109         buffer[i1--] = buffer[j1++];
39110         buffer[j2++] = buffer[i2--];
39111         buffer[i1--] = buffer[j1++];
39112         buffer[j2++] = buffer[i2--];
39113         buffer[i1--] = buffer[j1++];
39114         buffer[j2++] = buffer[i2--];
39115         buffer[i1--] = buffer[j1++];
39116         buffer[j2++] = buffer[i2--];
39117 
39118         this.filter(buffer, bufferPadding, width, u0, bufferOut);
39119 
39120         k = v * width;
39121         l = bufferPadding;
39122         for (var u = 0; u < width; u++, k++, l++)
39123           items[k] = bufferOut[l];
39124       }
39125 
39126       // Section F.3.5 VER_SR
39127       for (var u = 0; u < width; u++) {
39128         if (height == 1) {
39129           // if height = 1, when v0 even keep items as is, when odd divide by 2
39130           if ((v0 % 1) !== 0) {
39131             items[u] /= 2;
39132           }
39133           continue;
39134         }
39135 
39136         var k = u;
39137         var l = bufferPadding;
39138         for (var v = 0; v < height; v++, k += width, l++)
39139           buffer[l] = items[k];
39140 
39141         // Section F.3.7 extending... using max extension of 4
39142         var i1 = bufferPadding - 1, j1 = bufferPadding + 1;
39143         var i2 = bufferPadding + height - 2, j2 = bufferPadding + height;
39144         buffer[i1--] = buffer[j1++];
39145         buffer[j2++] = buffer[i2--];
39146         buffer[i1--] = buffer[j1++];
39147         buffer[j2++] = buffer[i2--];
39148         buffer[i1--] = buffer[j1++];
39149         buffer[j2++] = buffer[i2--];
39150         buffer[i1--] = buffer[j1++];
39151         buffer[j2++] = buffer[i2--];
39152 
39153         this.filter(buffer, bufferPadding, height, v0, bufferOut);
39154 
39155         k = u;
39156         l = bufferPadding;
39157         for (var v = 0; v < height; v++, k += width, l++)
39158           items[k] = bufferOut[l];
39159       }
39160       return {
39161         width: width,
39162         height: height,
39163         items: items
39164       };
39165     };
39166     return Transform;
39167   })();
39168 
39169   // Section 3.8.2 Irreversible 9-7 filter
39170   var IrreversibleTransform = (function IrreversibleTransformClosure() {
39171     function IrreversibleTransform() {
39172       Transform.call(this);
39173     }
39174 
39175     IrreversibleTransform.prototype = Object.create(Transform.prototype);
39176     IrreversibleTransform.prototype.filter =
39177       function irreversibleTransformFilter(y, offset, length, i0, x) {
39178       var i0_ = Math.floor(i0 / 2);
39179       var i1_ = Math.floor((i0 + length) / 2);
39180       var offset_ = offset - (i0 % 1);
39181 
39182       var alpha = -1.586134342059924;
39183       var beta = -0.052980118572961;
39184       var gamma = 0.882911075530934;
39185       var delta = 0.443506852043971;
39186       var K = 1.230174104914001;
39187       var K_ = 1 / K;
39188 
39189       // step 1
39190       var j = offset_ - 2;
39191       for (var n = i0_ - 1, nn = i1_ + 2; n < nn; n++, j += 2)
39192         x[j] = K * y[j];
39193 
39194       // step 2
39195       var j = offset_ - 3;
39196       for (var n = i0_ - 2, nn = i1_ + 2; n < nn; n++, j += 2)
39197         x[j] = K_ * y[j];
39198 
39199       // step 3
39200       var j = offset_ - 2;
39201       for (var n = i0_ - 1, nn = i1_ + 2; n < nn; n++, j += 2)
39202         x[j] -= delta * (x[j - 1] + x[j + 1]);
39203 
39204       // step 4
39205       var j = offset_ - 1;
39206       for (var n = i0_ - 1, nn = i1_ + 1; n < nn; n++, j += 2)
39207         x[j] -= gamma * (x[j - 1] + x[j + 1]);
39208 
39209       // step 5
39210       var j = offset_;
39211       for (var n = i0_, nn = i1_ + 1; n < nn; n++, j += 2)
39212         x[j] -= beta * (x[j - 1] + x[j + 1]);
39213 
39214       // step 6
39215       var j = offset_ + 1;
39216       for (var n = i0_, nn = i1_; n < nn; n++, j += 2)
39217         x[j] -= alpha * (x[j - 1] + x[j + 1]);
39218     };
39219 
39220     return IrreversibleTransform;
39221   })();
39222 
39223   // Section 3.8.1 Reversible 5-3 filter
39224   var ReversibleTransform = (function ReversibleTransformClosure() {
39225     function ReversibleTransform() {
39226       Transform.call(this);
39227     }
39228 
39229     ReversibleTransform.prototype = Object.create(Transform.prototype);
39230     ReversibleTransform.prototype.filter =
39231       function reversibleTransformFilter(y, offset, length, i0, x) {
39232       var i0_ = Math.floor(i0 / 2);
39233       var i1_ = Math.floor((i0 + length) / 2);
39234       var offset_ = offset - (i0 % 1);
39235 
39236       for (var n = i0_, nn = i1_ + 1, j = offset_; n < nn; n++, j += 2)
39237         x[j] = y[j] - Math.floor((y[j - 1] + y[j + 1] + 2) / 4);
39238 
39239       for (var n = i0_, nn = i1_, j = offset_ + 1; n < nn; n++, j += 2)
39240         x[j] = y[j] + Math.floor((x[j - 1] + x[j + 1]) / 2);
39241     };
39242 
39243     return ReversibleTransform;
39244   })();
