40882 var JpegImage = (function jpegImage() {
40883   "use strict";
40884   var dctZigZag = new Int32Array([
40885      0,
40886      1,  8,
40887     16,  9,  2,
40888      3, 10, 17, 24,
40889     32, 25, 18, 11, 4,
40890      5, 12, 19, 26, 33, 40,
40891     48, 41, 34, 27, 20, 13,  6,
40892      7, 14, 21, 28, 35, 42, 49, 56,
40893     57, 50, 43, 36, 29, 22, 15,
40894     23, 30, 37, 44, 51, 58,
40895     59, 52, 45, 38, 31,
40896     39, 46, 53, 60,
40897     61, 54, 47,
40898     55, 62,
40899     63
40900   ]);
40901 
40902   var dctCos1  =  4017   // cos(pi/16)
40903   var dctSin1  =   799   // sin(pi/16)
40904   var dctCos3  =  3406   // cos(3*pi/16)
40905   var dctSin3  =  2276   // sin(3*pi/16)
40906   var dctCos6  =  1567   // cos(6*pi/16)
40907   var dctSin6  =  3784   // sin(6*pi/16)
40908   var dctSqrt2 =  5793   // sqrt(2)
40909   var dctSqrt1d2 = 2896  // sqrt(2) / 2
40910 
40911   function constructor() {
40912   }
40913 
40914   function buildHuffmanTable(codeLengths, values) {
40915     var k = 0, code = [], i, j, length = 16;
40916     while (length > 0 && !codeLengths[length - 1])
40917       length--;
40918     code.push({children: [], index: 0});
40919     var p = code[0], q;
40920     for (i = 0; i < length; i++) {
40921       for (j = 0; j < codeLengths[i]; j++) {
40922         p = code.pop();
40923         p.children[p.index] = values[k];
40924         while (p.index > 0) {
40925           p = code.pop();
40926         }
40927         p.index++;
40928         code.push(p);
40929         while (code.length <= i) {
40930           code.push(q = {children: [], index: 0});
40931           p.children[p.index] = q.children;
40932           p = q;
40933         }
40934         k++;
40935       }
40936       if (i + 1 < length) {
40937         // p here points to last code
40938         code.push(q = {children: [], index: 0});
40939         p.children[p.index] = q.children;
40940         p = q;
40941       }
40942     }
40943     return code[0].children;
40944   }
40945 
40946   function decodeScan(data, offset,
40947                       frame, components, resetInterval,
40948                       spectralStart, spectralEnd,
40949                       successivePrev, successive) {
40950     var precision = frame.precision;
40951     var samplesPerLine = frame.samplesPerLine;
40952     var scanLines = frame.scanLines;
40953     var mcusPerLine = frame.mcusPerLine;
40954     var progressive = frame.progressive;
40955     var maxH = frame.maxH, maxV = frame.maxV;
40956 
40957     var startOffset = offset, bitsData = 0, bitsCount = 0;
40958     function readBit() {
40959       if (bitsCount > 0) {
40960         bitsCount--;
40961         return (bitsData >> bitsCount) & 1;
40962       }
40963       bitsData = data[offset++];
40964       if (bitsData == 0xFF) {
40965         var nextByte = data[offset++];
40966         if (nextByte) {
40967           throw "unexpected marker: " + ((bitsData << 8) | nextByte).toString(16);
40968         }
40969         // unstuff 0
40970       }
40971       bitsCount = 7;
40972       return bitsData >>> 7;
40973     }
40974     function decodeHuffman(tree) {
40975       var node = tree, bit;
40976       while ((bit = readBit()) !== null) {
40977         node = node[bit];
40978         if (typeof node === 'number')
40979           return node;
40980         if (typeof node !== 'object')
40981           throw "invalid huffman sequence";
40982       }
40983       return null;
40984     }
40985     function receive(length) {
40986       var n = 0;
40987       while (length > 0) {
40988         var bit = readBit();
40989         if (bit === null) return;
40990         n = (n << 1) | bit;
40991         length--;
40992       }
40993       return n;
40994     }
40995     function receiveAndExtend(length) {
40996       var n = receive(length);
40997       if (n >= 1 << (length - 1))
40998         return n;
40999       return n + (-1 << length) + 1;
41000     }
41001     function decodeBaseline(component, zz) {
41002       var t = decodeHuffman(component.huffmanTableDC);
41003       var diff = t === 0 ? 0 : receiveAndExtend(t);
41004       zz[0]= (component.pred += diff);
41005       var k = 1;
41006       while (k < 64) {
41007         var rs = decodeHuffman(component.huffmanTableAC);
41008         var s = rs & 15, r = rs >> 4;
41009         if (s === 0) {
41010           if (r < 15)
41011             break;
41012           k += 16;
41013           continue;
41014         }
41015         k += r;
41016         var z = dctZigZag[k];
41017         zz[z] = receiveAndExtend(s);
41018         k++;
41019       }
41020     }
41021     function decodeDCFirst(component, zz) {
41022       var t = decodeHuffman(component.huffmanTableDC);
41023       var diff = t === 0 ? 0 : (receiveAndExtend(t) << successive);
41024       zz[0] = (component.pred += diff);
41025     }
41026     function decodeDCSuccessive(component, zz) {
41027       zz[0] |= readBit() << successive;
41028     }
41029     var eobrun = 0;
41030     function decodeACFirst(component, zz) {
41031       if (eobrun > 0) {
41032         eobrun--;
41033         return;
41034       }
41035       var k = spectralStart, e = spectralEnd;
41036       while (k <= e) {
41037         var rs = decodeHuffman(component.huffmanTableAC);
41038         var s = rs & 15, r = rs >> 4;
41039         if (s === 0) {
41040           if (r < 15) {
41041             eobrun = receive(r) + (1 << r) - 1;
41042             break;
41043           }
41044           k += 16;
41045           continue;
41046         }
41047         k += r;
41048         var z = dctZigZag[k];
41049         zz[z] = receiveAndExtend(s) * (1 << successive);
41050         k++;
41051       }
41052     }
41053     var successiveACState = 0, successiveACNextValue;
41054     function decodeACSuccessive(component, zz) {
41055       var k = spectralStart, e = spectralEnd, r = 0;
41056       while (k <= e) {
41057         var z = dctZigZag[k];
41058         switch (successiveACState) {
41059         case 0: // initial state
41060           var rs = decodeHuffman(component.huffmanTableAC);
41061           var s = rs & 15, r = rs >> 4;
41062           if (s === 0) {
41063             if (r < 15) {
41064               eobrun = receive(r) + (1 << r);
41065               successiveACState = 4;
41066             } else {
41067               r = 16;
41068               successiveACState = 1;
41069             }
41070           } else {
41071             if (s !== 1)
41072               throw "invalid ACn encoding";
41073             successiveACNextValue = receiveAndExtend(s);
41074             successiveACState = r ? 2 : 3;
41075           }
41076           continue;
41077         case 1: // skipping r zero items
41078         case 2:
41079           if (zz[z])
41080             zz[z] += (readBit() << successive);
41081           else {
41082             r--;
41083             if (r === 0)
41084               successiveACState = successiveACState == 2 ? 3 : 0;
41085           }
41086           break;
41087         case 3: // set value for a zero item
41088           if (zz[z])
41089             zz[z] += (readBit() << successive);
41090           else {
41091             zz[z] = successiveACNextValue << successive;
41092             successiveACState = 0;
41093           }
41094           break;
41095         case 4: // eob
41096           if (zz[z])
41097             zz[z] += (readBit() << successive);
41098           break;
41099         }
41100         k++;
41101       }
41102       if (successiveACState === 4) {
41103         eobrun--;
41104         if (eobrun === 0)
41105           successiveACState = 0;
41106       }
41107     }
41108     function decodeMcu(component, decode, mcu, row, col) {
41109       var mcuRow = (mcu / mcusPerLine) | 0;
41110       var mcuCol = mcu % mcusPerLine;
41111       var blockRow = mcuRow * component.v + row;
41112       var blockCol = mcuCol * component.h + col;
41113       decode(component, component.blocks[blockRow][blockCol]);
41114     }
41115     function decodeBlock(component, decode, mcu) {
41116       var blockRow = (mcu / component.blocksPerLine) | 0;
41117       var blockCol = mcu % component.blocksPerLine;
41118       decode(component, component.blocks[blockRow][blockCol]);
41119     }
41120 
41121     var componentsLength = components.length;
41122     var component, i, j, k, n;
41123     var decodeFn;
41124     if (progressive) {
41125       if (spectralStart === 0)
41126         decodeFn = successivePrev === 0 ? decodeDCFirst : decodeDCSuccessive;
41127       else
41128         decodeFn = successivePrev === 0 ? decodeACFirst : decodeACSuccessive;
41129     } else {
41130       decodeFn = decodeBaseline;
41131     }
41132 
41133     var mcu = 0, marker;
41134     var mcuExpected;
41135     if (componentsLength == 1) {
41136       mcuExpected = components[0].blocksPerLine * components[0].blocksPerColumn;
41137     } else {
41138       mcuExpected = mcusPerLine * frame.mcusPerColumn;
41139     }
41140     if (!resetInterval) resetInterval = mcuExpected;
41141 
41142     var h, v;
41143     while (mcu < mcuExpected) {
41144       // reset interval stuff
41145       for (i = 0; i < componentsLength; i++)
41146         components[i].pred = 0;
41147       eobrun = 0;
41148 
41149       if (componentsLength == 1) {
41150         component = components[0];
41151         for (n = 0; n < resetInterval; n++) {
41152           decodeBlock(component, decodeFn, mcu);
41153           mcu++;
41154         }
41155       } else {
41156         for (n = 0; n < resetInterval; n++) {
41157           for (i = 0; i < componentsLength; i++) {
41158             component = components[i];
41159             h = component.h;
41160             v = component.v;
41161             for (j = 0; j < v; j++) {
41162               for (k = 0; k < h; k++) {
41163                 decodeMcu(component, decodeFn, mcu, j, k);
41164               }
41165             }
41166           }
41167           mcu++;
41168         }
41169       }
41170 
41171       // find marker
41172       bitsCount = 0;
41173       marker = (data[offset] << 8) | data[offset + 1];
41174       if (marker <= 0xFF00) {
41175         throw "marker was not found";
41176       }
41177 
41178       if (marker >= 0xFFD0 && marker <= 0xFFD7) { // RSTx
41179         offset += 2;
41180       }
41181       else
41182         break;
41183     }
41184 
41185     return offset - startOffset;
41186   }
41187 
41188   function buildComponentData(frame, component) {
41189     var lines = [];
41190     var blocksPerLine = component.blocksPerLine;
41191     var blocksPerColumn = component.blocksPerColumn;
41192     var samplesPerLine = blocksPerLine << 3;
41193     var R = new Int32Array(64), r = new Uint8Array(64);
41194 
41195     // A port of poppler's IDCT method which in turn is taken from:
41196     //   Christoph Loeffler, Adriaan Ligtenberg, George S. Moschytz,
41197     //   "Practical Fast 1-D DCT Algorithms with 11 Multiplications",
41198     //   IEEE Intl. Conf. on Acoustics, Speech & Signal Processing, 1989,
41199     //   988-991.
41200     function quantizeAndInverse(zz, dataOut, dataIn) {
41201       var qt = component.quantizationTable;
41202       var v0, v1, v2, v3, v4, v5, v6, v7, t;
41203       var p = dataIn;
41204       var i;
41205 
41206       // dequant
41207       for (i = 0; i < 64; i++)
41208         p[i] = zz[i] * qt[i];
41209 
41210       // inverse DCT on rows
41211       for (i = 0; i < 8; ++i) {
41212         var row = 8 * i;
41213 
41214         // check for all-zero AC coefficients
41215         if (p[1 + row] == 0 && p[2 + row] == 0 && p[3 + row] == 0 &&
41216             p[4 + row] == 0 && p[5 + row] == 0 && p[6 + row] == 0 &&
41217             p[7 + row] == 0) {
41218           t = (dctSqrt2 * p[0 + row] + 512) >> 10;
41219           p[0 + row] = t;
41220           p[1 + row] = t;
41221           p[2 + row] = t;
41222           p[3 + row] = t;
41223           p[4 + row] = t;
41224           p[5 + row] = t;
41225           p[6 + row] = t;
41226           p[7 + row] = t;
41227           continue;
41228         }
41229 
41230         // stage 4
41231         v0 = (dctSqrt2 * p[0 + row] + 128) >> 8;
41232         v1 = (dctSqrt2 * p[4 + row] + 128) >> 8;
41233         v2 = p[2 + row];
41234         v3 = p[6 + row];
41235         v4 = (dctSqrt1d2 * (p[1 + row] - p[7 + row]) + 128) >> 8;
41236         v7 = (dctSqrt1d2 * (p[1 + row] + p[7 + row]) + 128) >> 8;
41237         v5 = p[3 + row] << 4;
41238         v6 = p[5 + row] << 4;
41239 
41240         // stage 3
41241         t = (v0 - v1+ 1) >> 1;
41242         v0 = (v0 + v1 + 1) >> 1;
41243         v1 = t;
41244         t = (v2 * dctSin6 + v3 * dctCos6 + 128) >> 8;
41245         v2 = (v2 * dctCos6 - v3 * dctSin6 + 128) >> 8;
41246         v3 = t;
41247         t = (v4 - v6 + 1) >> 1;
41248         v4 = (v4 + v6 + 1) >> 1;
41249         v6 = t;
41250         t = (v7 + v5 + 1) >> 1;
41251         v5 = (v7 - v5 + 1) >> 1;
41252         v7 = t;
41253 
41254         // stage 2
41255         t = (v0 - v3 + 1) >> 1;
41256         v0 = (v0 + v3 + 1) >> 1;
41257         v3 = t;
41258         t = (v1 - v2 + 1) >> 1;
41259         v1 = (v1 + v2 + 1) >> 1;
41260         v2 = t;
41261         t = (v4 * dctSin3 + v7 * dctCos3 + 2048) >> 12;
41262         v4 = (v4 * dctCos3 - v7 * dctSin3 + 2048) >> 12;
41263         v7 = t;
41264         t = (v5 * dctSin1 + v6 * dctCos1 + 2048) >> 12;
41265         v5 = (v5 * dctCos1 - v6 * dctSin1 + 2048) >> 12;
41266         v6 = t;
41267 
41268         // stage 1
41269         p[0 + row] = v0 + v7;
41270         p[7 + row] = v0 - v7;
41271         p[1 + row] = v1 + v6;
41272         p[6 + row] = v1 - v6;
41273         p[2 + row] = v2 + v5;
41274         p[5 + row] = v2 - v5;
41275         p[3 + row] = v3 + v4;
41276         p[4 + row] = v3 - v4;
41277       }
41278 
41279       // inverse DCT on columns
41280       for (i = 0; i < 8; ++i) {
41281         var col = i;
41282 
41283         // check for all-zero AC coefficients
41284         if (p[1*8 + col] == 0 && p[2*8 + col] == 0 && p[3*8 + col] == 0 &&
41285             p[4*8 + col] == 0 && p[5*8 + col] == 0 && p[6*8 + col] == 0 &&
41286             p[7*8 + col] == 0) {
41287           t = (dctSqrt2 * dataIn[i+0] + 8192) >> 14;
41288           p[0*8 + col] = t;
41289           p[1*8 + col] = t;
41290           p[2*8 + col] = t;
41291           p[3*8 + col] = t;
41292           p[4*8 + col] = t;
41293           p[5*8 + col] = t;
41294           p[6*8 + col] = t;
41295           p[7*8 + col] = t;
41296           continue;
41297         }
41298 
41299         // stage 4
41300         v0 = (dctSqrt2 * p[0*8 + col] + 2048) >> 12;
41301         v1 = (dctSqrt2 * p[4*8 + col] + 2048) >> 12;
41302         v2 = p[2*8 + col];
41303         v3 = p[6*8 + col];
41304         v4 = (dctSqrt1d2 * (p[1*8 + col] - p[7*8 + col]) + 2048) >> 12;
41305         v7 = (dctSqrt1d2 * (p[1*8 + col] + p[7*8 + col]) + 2048) >> 12;
41306         v5 = p[3*8 + col];
41307         v6 = p[5*8 + col];
41308 
41309         // stage 3
41310         t = (v0 - v1 + 1) >> 1;
41311         v0 = (v0 + v1 + 1) >> 1;
41312         v1 = t;
41313         t = (v2 * dctSin6 + v3 * dctCos6 + 2048) >> 12;
41314         v2 = (v2 * dctCos6 - v3 * dctSin6 + 2048) >> 12;
41315         v3 = t;
41316         t = (v4 - v6 + 1) >> 1;
41317         v4 = (v4 + v6 + 1) >> 1;
41318         v6 = t;
41319         t = (v7 + v5 + 1) >> 1;
41320         v5 = (v7 - v5 + 1) >> 1;
41321         v7 = t;
41322 
41323         // stage 2
41324         t = (v0 - v3 + 1) >> 1;
41325         v0 = (v0 + v3 + 1) >> 1;
41326         v3 = t;
41327         t = (v1 - v2 + 1) >> 1;
41328         v1 = (v1 + v2 + 1) >> 1;
41329         v2 = t;
41330         t = (v4 * dctSin3 + v7 * dctCos3 + 2048) >> 12;
41331         v4 = (v4 * dctCos3 - v7 * dctSin3 + 2048) >> 12;
41332         v7 = t;
41333         t = (v5 * dctSin1 + v6 * dctCos1 + 2048) >> 12;
41334         v5 = (v5 * dctCos1 - v6 * dctSin1 + 2048) >> 12;
41335         v6 = t;
41336 
41337         // stage 1
41338         p[0*8 + col] = v0 + v7;
41339         p[7*8 + col] = v0 - v7;
41340         p[1*8 + col] = v1 + v6;
41341         p[6*8 + col] = v1 - v6;
41342         p[2*8 + col] = v2 + v5;
41343         p[5*8 + col] = v2 - v5;
41344         p[3*8 + col] = v3 + v4;
41345         p[4*8 + col] = v3 - v4;
41346       }
41347 
41348       // convert to 8-bit integers
41349       for (i = 0; i < 64; ++i) {
41350         var sample = 128 + ((p[i] + 8) >> 4);
41351         dataOut[i] = sample < 0 ? 0 : sample > 0xFF ? 0xFF : sample;
41352       }
41353     }
41354 
41355     var i, j;
41356     for (var blockRow = 0; blockRow < blocksPerColumn; blockRow++) {
41357       var scanLine = blockRow << 3;
41358       for (i = 0; i < 8; i++)
41359         lines.push(new Uint8Array(samplesPerLine));
41360       for (var blockCol = 0; blockCol < blocksPerLine; blockCol++) {
41361         quantizeAndInverse(component.blocks[blockRow][blockCol], r, R);
41362 
41363         var offset = 0, sample = blockCol << 3;
41364         for (j = 0; j < 8; j++) {
41365           var line = lines[scanLine + j];
41366           for (i = 0; i < 8; i++)
41367             line[sample + i] = r[offset++];
41368         }
41369       }
41370     }
41371     return lines;
41372   }
41373 
41374   function clampTo8bit(a) {
41375     return a < 0 ? 0 : a > 255 ? 255 : a;
41376   }
41377 
41378   constructor.prototype = {
41379     load: function load(path) {
41380       var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
41381       xhr.open("GET", path, true);
41382       xhr.responseType = "arraybuffer";
41383       xhr.onload = (function() {
41384         // TODO catch parse error
41385         var data = new Uint8Array(xhr.response || xhr.mozResponseArrayBuffer);
41386         this.parse(data);
41387         if (this.onload)
41388           this.onload();
41389       }).bind(this);
41390       xhr.send(null);
41391     },
41392     parse: function parse(data) {
41393       var offset = 0, length = data.length;
41394       function readUint16() {
41395         var value = (data[offset] << 8) | data[offset + 1];
41396         offset += 2;
41397         return value;
41398       }
41399       function readDataBlock() {
41400         var length = readUint16();
41401         var array = data.subarray(offset, offset + length - 2);
41402         offset += array.length;
41403         return array;
41404       }
41405       function prepareComponents(frame) {
41406         var maxH = 0, maxV = 0;
41407         var component, componentId;
41408         for (componentId in frame.components) {
41409           if (frame.components.hasOwnProperty(componentId)) {
41410             component = frame.components[componentId];
41411             if (maxH < component.h) maxH = component.h;
41412             if (maxV < component.v) maxV = component.v;
41413           }
41414         }
41415         var mcusPerLine = Math.ceil(frame.samplesPerLine / 8 / maxH);
41416         var mcusPerColumn = Math.ceil(frame.scanLines / 8 / maxV);
41417         for (componentId in frame.components) {
41418           if (frame.components.hasOwnProperty(componentId)) {
41419             component = frame.components[componentId];
41420             var blocksPerLine = Math.ceil(Math.ceil(frame.samplesPerLine / 8) * component.h / maxH);
41421             var blocksPerColumn = Math.ceil(Math.ceil(frame.scanLines  / 8) * component.v / maxV);
41422             var blocksPerLineForMcu = mcusPerLine * component.h;
41423             var blocksPerColumnForMcu = mcusPerColumn * component.v;
41424             var blocks = [];
41425             for (var i = 0; i < blocksPerColumnForMcu; i++) {
41426               var row = [];
41427               for (var j = 0; j < blocksPerLineForMcu; j++)
41428                 row.push(new Int32Array(64));
41429               blocks.push(row);
41430             }
41431             component.blocksPerLine = blocksPerLine;
41432             component.blocksPerColumn = blocksPerColumn;
41433             component.blocks = blocks;
41434           }
41435         }
41436         frame.maxH = maxH;
41437         frame.maxV = maxV;
41438         frame.mcusPerLine = mcusPerLine;
41439         frame.mcusPerColumn = mcusPerColumn;
41440       }
41441       var jfif = null;
41442       var adobe = null;
41443       var pixels = null;
41444       var frame, resetInterval;
41445       var quantizationTables = [], frames = [];
41446       var huffmanTablesAC = [], huffmanTablesDC = [];
41447       var fileMarker = readUint16();
41448       if (fileMarker != 0xFFD8) { // SOI (Start of Image)
41449         throw "SOI not found";
41450       }
41451 
41452       fileMarker = readUint16();
41453       while (fileMarker != 0xFFD9) { // EOI (End of image)
41454         var i, j, l;
41455         switch(fileMarker) {
41456           case 0xFFE0: // APP0 (Application Specific)
41457           case 0xFFE1: // APP1
41458           case 0xFFE2: // APP2
41459           case 0xFFE3: // APP3
41460           case 0xFFE4: // APP4
41461           case 0xFFE5: // APP5
41462           case 0xFFE6: // APP6
41463           case 0xFFE7: // APP7
41464           case 0xFFE8: // APP8
41465           case 0xFFE9: // APP9
41466           case 0xFFEA: // APP10
41467           case 0xFFEB: // APP11
41468           case 0xFFEC: // APP12
41469           case 0xFFED: // APP13
41470           case 0xFFEE: // APP14
41471           case 0xFFEF: // APP15
41472           case 0xFFFE: // COM (Comment)
41473             var appData = readDataBlock();
41474 
41475             if (fileMarker === 0xFFE0) {
41476               if (appData[0] === 0x4A && appData[1] === 0x46 && appData[2] === 0x49 &&
41477                 appData[3] === 0x46 && appData[4] === 0) { // 'JFIF\x00'
41478                 jfif = {
41479                   version: { major: appData[5], minor: appData[6] },
41480                   densityUnits: appData[7],
41481                   xDensity: (appData[8] << 8) | appData[9],
41482                   yDensity: (appData[10] << 8) | appData[11],
41483                   thumbWidth: appData[12],
41484                   thumbHeight: appData[13],
41485                   thumbData: appData.subarray(14, 14 + 3 * appData[12] * appData[13])
41486                 };
41487               }
41488             }
41489             // TODO APP1 - Exif
41490             if (fileMarker === 0xFFEE) {
41491               if (appData[0] === 0x41 && appData[1] === 0x64 && appData[2] === 0x6F &&
41492                 appData[3] === 0x62 && appData[4] === 0x65 && appData[5] === 0) { // 'Adobe\x00'
41493                 adobe = {
41494                   version: appData[6],
41495                   flags0: (appData[7] << 8) | appData[8],
41496                   flags1: (appData[9] << 8) | appData[10],
41497                   transformCode: appData[11]
41498                 };
41499               }
41500             }
41501             break;
41502 
41503           case 0xFFDB: // DQT (Define Quantization Tables)
41504             var quantizationTablesLength = readUint16();
41505             var quantizationTablesEnd = quantizationTablesLength + offset - 2;
41506             while (offset < quantizationTablesEnd) {
41507               var quantizationTableSpec = data[offset++];
41508               var tableData = new Int32Array(64);
41509               if ((quantizationTableSpec >> 4) === 0) { // 8 bit values
41510                 for (j = 0; j < 64; j++) {
41511                   var z = dctZigZag[j];
41512                   tableData[z] = data[offset++];
41513                 }
41514               } else if ((quantizationTableSpec >> 4) === 1) { //16 bit
41515                 for (j = 0; j < 64; j++) {
41516                   var z = dctZigZag[j];
41517                   tableData[z] = readUint16();
41518                 }
41519               } else
41520                 throw "DQT: invalid table spec";
41521               quantizationTables[quantizationTableSpec & 15] = tableData;
41522             }
41523             break;
41524 
41525           case 0xFFC0: // SOF0 (Start of Frame, Baseline DCT)
41526           case 0xFFC1: // SOF1 (Start of Frame, Extended DCT)
41527           case 0xFFC2: // SOF2 (Start of Frame, Progressive DCT)
41528             readUint16(); // skip data length
41529             frame = {};
41530             frame.extended = (fileMarker === 0xFFC1);
41531             frame.progressive = (fileMarker === 0xFFC2);
41532             frame.precision = data[offset++];
41533             frame.scanLines = readUint16();
41534             frame.samplesPerLine = readUint16();
41535             frame.components = {};
41536             frame.componentsOrder = [];
41537             var componentsCount = data[offset++], componentId;
41538             var maxH = 0, maxV = 0;
41539             for (i = 0; i < componentsCount; i++) {
41540               componentId = data[offset];
41541               var h = data[offset + 1] >> 4;
41542               var v = data[offset + 1] & 15;
41543               var qId = data[offset + 2];
41544               frame.componentsOrder.push(componentId);
41545               frame.components[componentId] = {
41546                 h: h,
41547                 v: v,
41548                 quantizationTable: quantizationTables[qId]
41549               };
41550               offset += 3;
41551             }
41552             prepareComponents(frame);
41553             frames.push(frame);
41554             break;
41555 
41556           case 0xFFC4: // DHT (Define Huffman Tables)
41557             var huffmanLength = readUint16();
41558             for (i = 2; i < huffmanLength;) {
41559               var huffmanTableSpec = data[offset++];
41560               var codeLengths = new Uint8Array(16);
41561               var codeLengthSum = 0;
41562               for (j = 0; j < 16; j++, offset++)
41563                 codeLengthSum += (codeLengths[j] = data[offset]);
41564               var huffmanValues = new Uint8Array(codeLengthSum);
41565               for (j = 0; j < codeLengthSum; j++, offset++)
41566                 huffmanValues[j] = data[offset];
41567               i += 17 + codeLengthSum;
41568 
41569               ((huffmanTableSpec >> 4) === 0 ? 
41570                 huffmanTablesDC : huffmanTablesAC)[huffmanTableSpec & 15] =
41571                 buildHuffmanTable(codeLengths, huffmanValues);
41572             }
41573             break;
41574 
41575           case 0xFFDD: // DRI (Define Restart Interval)
41576             readUint16(); // skip data length
41577             resetInterval = readUint16();
41578             break;
41579 
41580           case 0xFFDA: // SOS (Start of Scan)
41581             var scanLength = readUint16();
41582             var selectorsCount = data[offset++];
41583             var components = [], component;
41584             for (i = 0; i < selectorsCount; i++) {
41585               component = frame.components[data[offset++]];
41586               var tableSpec = data[offset++];
41587               component.huffmanTableDC = huffmanTablesDC[tableSpec >> 4];
41588               component.huffmanTableAC = huffmanTablesAC[tableSpec & 15];
41589               components.push(component);
41590             }
41591             var spectralStart = data[offset++];
41592             var spectralEnd = data[offset++];
41593             var successiveApproximation = data[offset++];
41594             var processed = decodeScan(data, offset,
41595               frame, components, resetInterval,
41596               spectralStart, spectralEnd,
41597               successiveApproximation >> 4, successiveApproximation & 15);
41598             offset += processed;
41599             break;
41600           default:
41601             if (data[offset - 3] == 0xFF &&
41602                 data[offset - 2] >= 0xC0 && data[offset - 2] <= 0xFE) {
41603               // could be incorrect encoding -- last 0xFF byte of the previous
41604               // block was eaten by the encoder
41605               offset -= 3;
41606               break;
41607             }
41608             throw "unknown JPEG marker " + fileMarker.toString(16);
41609         }
41610         fileMarker = readUint16();
41611       }
41612       if (frames.length != 1)
41613         throw "only single frame JPEGs supported";
41614 
41615       this.width = frame.samplesPerLine;
41616       this.height = frame.scanLines;
41617       this.jfif = jfif;
41618       this.adobe = adobe;
41619       this.components = [];
41620       for (var i = 0; i < frame.componentsOrder.length; i++) {
41621         var component = frame.components[frame.componentsOrder[i]];
41622         this.components.push({
41623           lines: buildComponentData(frame, component),
41624           scaleX: component.h / frame.maxH,
41625           scaleY: component.v / frame.maxV
41626         });
41627       }
41628     },
41629     getData: function getData(width, height) {
41630       var scaleX = this.width / width, scaleY = this.height / height;
41631 
41632       var component1, component2, component3, component4;
41633       var component1Line, component2Line, component3Line, component4Line;
41634       var x, y;
41635       var offset = 0;
41636       var Y, Cb, Cr, K, C, M, Ye, R, G, B;
41637       var colorTransform;
41638       var dataLength = width * height * this.components.length;
41639       var data = new Uint8Array(dataLength);
41640       switch (this.components.length) {
41641         case 1:
41642           component1 = this.components[0];
41643           for (y = 0; y < height; y++) {
41644             component1Line = component1.lines[0 | (y * component1.scaleY * scaleY)];
41645             for (x = 0; x < width; x++) {
41646               Y = component1Line[0 | (x * component1.scaleX * scaleX)];
41647 
41648               data[offset++] = Y;
41649             }
41650           }
41651           break;
41652         case 2:
41653           // PDF might compress two component data in custom colorspace
41654           component1 = this.components[0];
41655           component2 = this.components[1];
41656           for (y = 0; y < height; y++) {
41657             component1Line = component1.lines[0 | (y * component1.scaleY * scaleY)];
41658             component2Line = component1.lines[0 | (y * component2.scaleY * scaleY)];
41659             for (x = 0; x < width; x++) {
41660               Y = component1Line[0 | (x * component1.scaleX * scaleX)];
41661               data[offset++] = Y;
41662               Y = component2Line[0 | (x * component2.scaleX * scaleX)];
41663               data[offset++] = Y;
41664             }
41665           }
41666           break;
41667         case 3:
41668           // The default transform for three components is true
41669           colorTransform = true;
41670           // The adobe transform marker overrides any previous setting
41671           if (this.adobe && this.adobe.transformCode)
41672             colorTransform = true;
41673           else if (typeof this.colorTransform !== 'undefined')
41674             colorTransform = !!this.colorTransform;
41675 
41676           component1 = this.components[0];
41677           component2 = this.components[1];
41678           component3 = this.components[2];
41679           for (y = 0; y < height; y++) {
41680             component1Line = component1.lines[0 | (y * component1.scaleY * scaleY)];
41681             component2Line = component2.lines[0 | (y * component2.scaleY * scaleY)];
41682             component3Line = component3.lines[0 | (y * component3.scaleY * scaleY)];
41683             for (x = 0; x < width; x++) {
41684               if (!colorTransform) {
41685                 R = component1Line[0 | (x * component1.scaleX * scaleX)];
41686                 G = component2Line[0 | (x * component2.scaleX * scaleX)];
41687                 B = component3Line[0 | (x * component3.scaleX * scaleX)];
41688               } else {
41689                 Y = component1Line[0 | (x * component1.scaleX * scaleX)];
41690                 Cb = component2Line[0 | (x * component2.scaleX * scaleX)];
41691                 Cr = component3Line[0 | (x * component3.scaleX * scaleX)];
41692 
41693                 R = clampTo8bit(Y + 1.402 * (Cr - 128));
41694                 G = clampTo8bit(Y - 0.3441363 * (Cb - 128) - 0.71413636 * (Cr - 128));
41695                 B = clampTo8bit(Y + 1.772 * (Cb - 128));
41696               }
41697 
41698               data[offset++] = R;
41699               data[offset++] = G;
41700               data[offset++] = B;
41701             }
41702           }
41703           break;
41704         case 4:
41705           // The default transform for four components is false
41706           colorTransform = false;
41707           // The adobe transform marker overrides any previous setting
41708           if (this.adobe && this.adobe.transformCode)
41709             colorTransform = true;
41710           else if (typeof this.colorTransform !== 'undefined')
41711             colorTransform = !!this.colorTransform;
41712 
41713           component1 = this.components[0];
41714           component2 = this.components[1];
41715           component3 = this.components[2];
41716           component4 = this.components[3];
41717           for (y = 0; y < height; y++) {
41718             component1Line = component1.lines[0 | (y * component1.scaleY * scaleY)];
41719             component2Line = component2.lines[0 | (y * component2.scaleY * scaleY)];
41720             component3Line = component3.lines[0 | (y * component3.scaleY * scaleY)];
41721             component4Line = component4.lines[0 | (y * component4.scaleY * scaleY)];
41722             for (x = 0; x < width; x++) {
41723               if (!colorTransform) {
41724                 C = component1Line[0 | (x * component1.scaleX * scaleX)];
41725                 M = component2Line[0 | (x * component2.scaleX * scaleX)];
41726                 Ye = component3Line[0 | (x * component3.scaleX * scaleX)];
41727                 K = component4Line[0 | (x * component4.scaleX * scaleX)];
41728               } else {
41729                 Y = component1Line[0 | (x * component1.scaleX * scaleX)];
41730                 Cb = component2Line[0 | (x * component2.scaleX * scaleX)];
41731                 Cr = component3Line[0 | (x * component3.scaleX * scaleX)];
41732                 K = component4Line[0 | (x * component4.scaleX * scaleX)];
41733 
41734                 C = 255 - clampTo8bit(Y + 1.402 * (Cr - 128));
41735                 M = 255 - clampTo8bit(Y - 0.3441363 * (Cb - 128) - 0.71413636 * (Cr - 128));
41736                 Ye = 255 - clampTo8bit(Y + 1.772 * (Cb - 128));
41737               }
41738               data[offset++] = C;
41739               data[offset++] = M;
41740               data[offset++] = Ye;
41741               data[offset++] = K;
41742             }
41743           }
41744           break;
41745         default:
41746           throw 'Unsupported color mode';
41747       }
41748       return data;
41749     },
41750     copyToImageData: function copyToImageData(imageData) {
41751       var width = imageData.width, height = imageData.height;
41752       var imageDataArray = imageData.data;
41753       var data = this.getData(width, height);
41754       var i = 0, j = 0, x, y;
41755       var Y, K, C, M, R, G, B;
41756       switch (this.components.length) {
41757         case 1:
41758           for (y = 0; y < height; y++) {
41759             for (x = 0; x < width; x++) {
41760               Y = data[i++];
41761 
41762               imageDataArray[j++] = Y;
41763               imageDataArray[j++] = Y;
41764               imageDataArray[j++] = Y;
41765               imageDataArray[j++] = 255;
41766             }
41767           }
41768           break;
41769         case 3:
41770           for (y = 0; y < height; y++) {
41771             for (x = 0; x < width; x++) {
41772               R = data[i++];
41773               G = data[i++];
41774               B = data[i++];
41775 
41776               imageDataArray[j++] = R;
41777               imageDataArray[j++] = G;
41778               imageDataArray[j++] = B;
41779               imageDataArray[j++] = 255;
41780             }
41781           }
41782           break;
41783         case 4:
41784           for (y = 0; y < height; y++) {
41785             for (x = 0; x < width; x++) {
41786               C = data[i++];
41787               M = data[i++];
41788               Y = data[i++];
41789               K = data[i++];
41790 
41791               R = 255 - clampTo8bit(C * (1 - K / 255) + K);
41792               G = 255 - clampTo8bit(M * (1 - K / 255) + K);
41793               B = 255 - clampTo8bit(Y * (1 - K / 255) + K);
41794 
41795               imageDataArray[j++] = R;
41796               imageDataArray[j++] = G;
41797               imageDataArray[j++] = B;
41798               imageDataArray[j++] = 255;
41799             }
41800           }
41801           break;
41802         default:
41803           throw 'Unsupported color mode';
41804       }
41805     }
41806   };
